NG0859:6695: khyad par ci yang med par 'gyur //
NG0859:6696: de phyir ngas gsang snying po 'di //
NG0859:6697: mun pa las ni mar me'am //
NG0859:6698: ba blang rnams las glang chen nam /
NG0859:6699: gcan gzan rnams las seng ge'am //
NG0859:6700: rkang thang rnams las rta ba bzhin //
NG0859:6701: kun gyi nang nas khyad par 'phags //
NG0859:6704: gdod ma nyid nas grol zhing ka nas dag pa'i
NG0859:6705: chos nyid la nyi tshe ba'i blta bya'i yul dang
NG0859:6706: */ lta byed kyi shes pa gnyis su chad pas 'khrul ma 'khrul dang */
NG0859:6707: rtogs ma rtogs su bsgrubs pa'i ltos gzhi dang */
NG0859:6708: ltos pa'i chos las log pas /

NG0859:6710: yang dag pa ma yin par mnyam zhing tha snyad tsam du btags pa las /

NG0859:6717: thams cad yang dag yang dag min //

NG0859:6723: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal ba //

NG0859:6726: chos dang chos nyid yang med de //

NG0859:6734: bdaganyid can du 'gyur bas srid pa'i rtsa ba 'byin
NG0859:6737: rgyal ba rnams kyi stong nyid ni //

NG0859:6795: mtshan nyid snang ba bzhis 'bras bu phyis dus la

NG0859:6800: sha lo ka 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NG0859:6803: gzer bu brgya dang brgyad cu //

NG0859:6807: bya dang brjod byed nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par
NG0859:6808: bka' stsal / man ngag gi sde de gsum ka'ang klong gsum du 'du ste /
NG0859:6809: rol pa 'gag pa med pa'i klong */

NG0859:7520: gzhon nu dpa' bo stobs ldan dang */

NG0859:7524: dus kyi 'khor lo sogs rdo rje'i gnas gang ston
NG0859:7525: pa de'i gtso bo'i rnam pa dang rnam 'gyur las
NG0859:7526: 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor sprul te na da mi shigs

NG0859:7529: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste //
NG0859:7530: 'chad dang nyan pa'ang nga nyid yin //
NG0859:7533: 'chad pa po nga chos kyang nga *//
NG0859:7534: rang gi tshogs ldan nyan pa'ang nga *//
NG0859:7535: zhes gsungs pa'i tshul gyis so /

NG0859:7539: sham+b+ha la la sogs kun rdzob kyi gnas rnams su'ang bya ba dang */

NG0859:7544: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NG0859:7545: so sor 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NG0859:7546: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang *//
NG0859:7547: las kyi dbang gis so sor snang *//
NG0859:7549: de'i phyir 'og min sogs dag pa'i zhing khams rnams su rang bzhin gnyis su med pa dang */
NG0859:7550: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor la gsang sngags
NG0859:7551: kyi chos 'khor bskor bar mdzad pa de las ma

NG0859:7553: rnam pas mdzad pa bcu gnyis bstan pa dang */
NG0859:7554: gdul bya dag ma dag sna tshogs la ci rigs
NG0859:7555: par theg pa gsum gyi chos kyi 'khor lo rim
NG0859:7556: pa gsum du bskor bar snang ste /
NG0859:7559: byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba rig pa'i skyes bu
NG0859:7560: thub pa drug de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs
NG0859:7562: thon nas kyang las kyis dbang gis snrel gzhi dang
NG0859:7563: yas man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha'
NG0859:7564: med pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po re rer
NG0859:7565: thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res 'dul
NG0859:7566: ba rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba lnga'i don mdzad do
NG0859:7568: 'jam dpal sgyu dra'i bshad rgyud las /
NG0859:7569: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NG0859:7570: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NG0859:7572: byang chub sems dpa' lha rnams dang *//
NG0859:7573: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NG0859:7574: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang *//
NG0859:7575: sprul sku 'khor los sgyur ba dang *//
NG0859:7576: shakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NG0859:7577: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i tshe //
NG0859:7580: gzhan yang slob dpon nyi 'ong seng ges 'og min
NG0859:7581: du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus rdo rje theg pa
NG0859:7582: ston pa dang dus mtshungs par mi yul du mchog
NG0859:7583: gi sprul skus byang chub snying po rdo rje gdan
NG0859:7584: du 'tshang rgya tshul ma bstan pa'i gong rol du

NG0859:7586: 'gram du bzhag nas ye shes kyi lus 'og min
NG0859:7587: du gshegs pa la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NG0859:7589: rdo rje dbyings chen por sangs rgyas te ri rab
NG0859:7590: kyi rtse dang rgya mtsho'i 'gram du yo ga'i rgyud
NG0859:7591: rnams gsungs / de nas au di ya na dang
NG0859:7592: sa ho ra'i yul rnams su gshegs nas in+d+ra b+hu
NG0859:7593: ti la sogs pa rnams la gsang sngags bla med
NG0859:7594: kyi rgyud sde thams cad bstan nas /
NG0859:7595: slar btags pa'i lus la zhugs te rdo rje gdan du 'tshang rgya ba'i tshul bstan par bzhed la /
NG0859:7596: de dang mthun par slob dpon ye shes zhabs kyis kyang */
NG0859:7597: de don ma rtogs nai rany+dzar //
NG0859:7598: ci yang ma yin ting 'dzin gnas //
NG0859:7599: de tshe bde gshegs kun gyis kyang *//
NG0859:7600: thal byung blo can de bzlog ste //
NG0859:7601: nam mkha'i dbyings ltar rnam dag pa'i //
NG0859:7602: zab gsal gnyis med rab bstan te //
NG0859:7603: nam phyed dus su rgyal ba ltar //
NG0859:7604: de nyid bsgoms pas tho rengs su //
NG0859:7605: skad cig gis ni yang dag rtogs //
NG0859:7606: byang chub snying por bzhugs byas nas //
NG0859:7607: mthu chen bdud rnams rab bcom ste //
NG0859:7608: sems can gzung bar bya ba'i phyir //
NG0859:7611: slob dpon chen po sgeg pa'i rdo rjes /
NG0859:7612: ston pas 'og min du gsang sngags ston pa dang
NG0859:7613: dus gcig tu mchog gi sprul skus 'jig rten tu
NG0859:7614: thun mong gi theg pa bshad par bzhed de /
NG0859:7615: des mdzad pa'i snying po'i 'grel pa spar khab tu /
NG0859:7616: drug pa'i ston pa lhun gyis grub pa'i thabs dang */
NG0859:7617: smon lam gyis go phyes nas /
NG0859:7618: le'u dang por rgyu snang bar mdzad /
NG0859:7621: bca' gzhi'i ston pa drug snang ba mdzad de dus mtshungs par tha dad pa'i rgyud rnams byung ba'o //
NG0859:7622: zhes bshad pa 'dis mdo dang sngags kyi sde snod
NG0859:7623: thams cad sdud par 'gyur la rang re theg chen
NG0859:7624: nges don la mos pa lam du byed ba rnams
NG0859:7625: kyis ston pa gdod ma'i mgon po gcig las tha
NG0859:7627: chos kyi 'khor lo ji snyed cig dus gcig tu
NG0859:7628: bskor ba yang gdul bya'i bsam pa'i dbang gis tha
NG0859:7629: dad ltar snang ba las dus snga phyi sogs rnam
NG0859:7630: gzhag sgrig tu med par shes par bya ba nyid
NG0859:7631: legs so // gnyis pa bka' de rnams bsdus pa po so sos bsdus tshul ni /
NG0859:7632: bla med kyi rgyud rnams phal cher sdud pa po
NG0859:7633: tha dad ltar bstan kyang bye brag rdzogs pa chen
NG0859:7634: po nges gsang man ngag gi sde rnams dang */
NG0859:7635: gsang ba snying po sogs rgyud sde 'ga' zhig ston 'khor dgongs pa tha mi dad pa'i phyir /
NG0859:7637: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa zhes 'byung ba dang */
NG0859:7638: bde mchog rtsa rgyud las kyang */
NG0859:7639: de nas gsang ba bshad par bya /
NG0859:7640: zhes 'byung ba ste 'di skad bdag gis bshad pa'am
NG0859:7641: thos pa la sogs pa rgyud don ma lus pa
NG0859:7642: mtshon pa'i tshig 'phrad de rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don
NG0859:7643: thams cad tshang ba'i phyir ram /
NG0859:7644: gleng slong gi skabs lhan cig pa'i 'khor rgyun mtha'i
NG0859:7645: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la gtso bo yab yum
NG0859:7646: gyis yab kyi thabs kyi cha dang yum gyis shes
NG0859:7647: rab kyi cha bzung nas sbyor ba'i lam gyis 'dod
NG0859:7648: chags chen po'i dbang bskur ba dang thabs shes dbyer
NG0859:7649: med kyi cha bzung nas zab pa'i dbang gsum bskur
NG0859:7650: ba'i mthar khu rdul rlung gsum 'gyur bde myong ba'i
NG0859:7651: sems dang bcas pa bcom pas ston 'khor dgongs pa
NG0859:7652: dbyer med du gyur pa thun mong ma yin pa'i
NG0859:7653: gleng slong du bshad pa ste /
NG0859:7655: rgyud rnams dag las 'di skad bdag gis thos zhes
NG0859:7656: gsungs pa gang de 'di ltar bdag gis shes pa
NG0859:7657: ste / rdo rje can ni zla ba zhu las
NG0859:7658: rdo rje gang zhig spyi mgrin snying ga'i chu skyes
NG0859:7659: ste / lte gsang dang *// thugs med rnams kyi
NG0859:7660: b+ha gar de yi thig le grol ba gsum gyis
NG0859:7661: mchog gi pad+ma la gnas pa //
NG0859:7662: deng 'dir sangs rgyas zhing du rab tu bzhugs pa
NG0859:7663: bcom ldan 'das su rnal 'byor rnams kyis rig par
NG0859:7665: dbang rnon gyi gdul byas 'di nyid kho nas rgyud
NG0859:7666: don rdzogs par rtogs par bshad pa'i phyir sdud pa
NG0859:7667: pos sbyar ba'i tshig kho nar mtha' gcig tu 'dod
NG0859:7668: pa mi legs shing 'di skad bdag gis thos pa
NG0859:7669: zhes 'khor gyi tshig ltar ma smos pas rgyud ma
NG0859:7671: dpal gsang ba grub pa'i rgyud las //
NG0859:7672: 'di yi sdud par byed pa po //
NG0859:7673: gzhan dag yod pa ma yin te //
NG0859:7674: bdag nyid 'ba' zhig smra bar byed //
NG0859:7675: rgyud mdzad pa ni thugs rdo rje //
NG0859:7680: zhes pa la sogs gsungs pa'i phyir sdud pa po
NG0859:7681: yang ston pa nyid las gzhan du ma gyur te
NG0859:7683: rgyun 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje //
NG0859:7684: 'chad pa po de sdud pa'ang de //
NG0859:7686: gzhan yang de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs kyi
NG0859:7687: gsang ba 'dzin pa dang bka'i bsdu ba po byang
NG0859:7688: chub sems dpa' chen po lag na rdo rje ni
NG0859:7689: ston 'khor gang du bshad kyang mi 'gal te /
NG0859:7690: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs rdo rje las gzhan du ma gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NG0859:7691: de bas na rdzogs pa chen po sogs rgyud rnams phal mo che gsang ba'i bdag po dang */
NG0859:7696: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje la sogs pa rnams dang */
NG0859:7697: mkha' 'gro ma purna nye bar zhi ba la sogs /
NG0859:7700: gzhan yang gdul bya lha dang */
NG0859:7702: gnod sbyin la sogs rigs can ma nges pa'i tshogs kyis bsdu bar mdzad la /
NG0859:7703: mtha' dag pa'i rgyud rnams gsang ba'i bdag po kho
NG0859:7704: nas bsdus par yang rung ste bde bar gshegs pas
NG0859:7705: gsang sngags kyi bstan pa gtad cing ma 'ongs pa
NG0859:7706: na 'jig rten du gsang sngags sgrogs par dbang bskur
NG0859:7707: ba dang */ sangs rgyas rnams kyi rdo rje'i snyan
NG0859:7708: gcig tu bsdus par gsungs pa dang rgyud sde rnams
NG0859:7709: glegs bam la 'god par rjes su gnang ba sogs
NG0859:7710: drug pa'i rgyal tshab chen po yin pa'i phyir te
NG0859:7712: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NG0859:7713: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //
NG0859:7714: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba'i phyir //
NG0859:7715: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NG0859:7716: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung *//
NG0859:7717: zhes bstan pa gtad pa dang */
NG0859:7718: ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NG0859:7719: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su gsang ba'i rgyud skal ba dang ldan pa rnams la sus 'chad par byed /
NG0859:7721: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad par byed /
NG0859:7723: in+d+ra b+hu ti'i bde mchog rtsa rgyud kyi 'grel pa las /
NG0859:7724: rgyud rnams ma lus sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs //
NG0859:7725: bye ba phrag ni dgu bcu rtsa drug sogs //

NG0859:7727: gsol ba btab tshe 'di skad bdag thos zhes //
NG0859:7728: rab tu gsungs pa gser gyi glegs bam la //
NG0859:7729: baidur+ya ni zhun mas yi ger bkod //
NG0859:7731: bye brag rgyud rnams zhu ba po gang yin pa de nyid bsdu ba po yang yin te /
NG0859:7733: brtag gnyis rdo rje snying po /
NG0859:7735: rdo rje mkha' 'gro phag mo bsdus pa bzhin no //
NG0859:7736: de dang dus mtshungs par rgyu'i theg chen gyi mdo
NG0859:7737: sde rnams kyang byang chub sems dpa' gtso bo gtso
NG0859:7738: bor dag dang gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NG0859:7739: 'dun lnga brgya dag gis bsdus par bshad cing */
NG0859:7741: mchog gi sprul sku mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og
NG0859:7742: tu nyan thos dgra bcom pa gtso bo rnams dang
NG0859:7743: so skye ci rigs pa dag gis theg dman gyi
NG0859:7744: sde snod gsum kyang ji snyed pa bsdu ba byas
NG0859:7745: so // gnyis pa bstan pa de nyid 'jig rten du ji ltar byung ba'i tshul la gnyis te /
NG0859:7747: gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa'o //
NG0859:7749: rig 'dzin mi ma yin pa dang */
NG0859:7750: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka las byung ba'o //
NG0859:7752: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor de dag gi nang nas
NG0859:7753: ston pa nyid kyis sprul pa rigs gsum du snang
NG0859:7754: bar mdzad pa des gdul bya lha klu gnod sbyin
NG0859:7755: gsum la brda'i sgo nas bshad cing bstan pa ste
NG0859:7756: / 'jam dpal gyis gtso bor zab mo phyogs kyis gdul bya'i don mdzad pas lta ba'i phyogs ston /

NG0859:7758: phyag na rdo rjes thabs la mkhas pas drag shul
NG0859:7759: phyogs kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas spyod pa'i phyogs
NG0859:7760: ston / de yang 'jam dpal gyis lha'i gnas su lha grags ldan mchog skyong la bshad /

NG0859:7762: des skye dgu'i bdag po tshangs pa dang */
NG0859:7765: dbang po brgya byin sogs lha'i rig pa 'dzin pa tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad /
NG0859:7766: spyan ras gzigs kyis klu'i gnas su klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad /
NG0859:7767: de nas klu mo kha 'dul ma dang */
NG0859:7770: 'jog po sogs klu'i rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad /
NG0859:7771: phyag na rdo rjes gnod sbyin gyi gnas su gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la bshad /
NG0859:7772: de nas gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje dang */
NG0859:7773: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdongs sogs gnod sbyin gyi rig 'dzin tshom bu 'bum sde la bshad cing */
NG0859:7774: de dag rnams kyis so so'i 'khor kyi tshogs la'ang
NG0859:7775: bshad pas tshom bu dang bcas pas rdo rje 'chang
NG0859:7776: gi sa brnyes par gyur to //
NG0859:7777: rdzogs pa chen po'i skor ni sum cu rtsa gsum
NG0859:7778: gyi lha de ba bzang skyong gi bu lhag sems
NG0859:7779: can la rmi ltas khyad par can bzhi byung ba
NG0859:7780: dang mthun par phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NG0859:7781: thams cad dang rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis
NG0859:7782: rdo rje sems dpa' byin gyis brlabs pa la brten
NG0859:7783: nas / rdo rje sems dpas lha'i bu lhag sems
NG0859:7784: can la rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang bskur zhing
NG0859:7785: rdzogs pa chen po'i man ngag rnams gnang nas lha
NG0859:7786: yul du dar bar gyur to //
NG0859:7787: de yang ye shes zhabs kyi grol thig tu /
NG0859:7788: de nas bzung ste don mchog 'di //
NG0859:7789: skal bar ldan pa 'ga' zhig la //
NG0859:7790: zhal nas zhal dang snyan nas snyan //
NG0859:7791: brgyud de nges pa'i don bstan pa'o //
NG0859:7795: dgongs pa lung ston pa'i mdo las /
NG0859:7796: 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum po dag / bcom ldan nges par gsungs lags na //
NG0859:7797: rgyu 'bras lhun grub tu spyod cing *//
NG0859:7798: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NG0859:7799: nges pa'i theg pa cis ma gsungs //
NG0859:7801: rgyu la mos par rgyu'i chos kyi //
NG0859:7802: 'khor lo rab tu bkor byas nas //
NG0859:7803: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig / ma 'ongs dus nas 'byung bar 'gyur //
NG0859:7805: ston pa mchog gi sprul sku mya ngan las 'das
NG0859:7806: nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'das pa na lha
NG0859:7810: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NG0859:7811: mi'i rig 'dzin li tsa bi dri ma med par grags pa ste /
NG0859:7812: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga pos 'jig rten
NG0859:7813: na mgon po yongs su mya ngan las 'das par
NG0859:7814: rang gi mngon par shes pas shes nas nang du
NG0859:7815: yang dag par 'jog pa las langs te lang+ka'i yul
NG0859:7816: gyi ri ma la ya'i rtse mor rdzu 'phrul gyis
NG0859:7820: ston pa sgron ma'i 'od nub tshe //
NG0859:7821: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis bsal //
NG0859:7822: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdung tshig nyi shu rtsa gsum bton cing rma ga chad par ngus so //
NG0859:7823: gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jig rten na
NG0859:7824: gsang sngags kyi sgra yongs su grags pa phyis 'byung
NG0859:7825: bar lung bstan pa bzhin dus la bab pa de'i
NG0859:7826: tshe gsang ba'i bdag po lag na rdo rjes sangs
NG0859:7827: rgyas kyis gsang sngags ston par dbang bskur ba brnyes
NG0859:7828: pa'i phyir der mngon sum du snang bar mdzad nas
NG0859:7829: rigs can lnga dang gzhan yang rig pa 'dzin pa'i
NG0859:7830: dge 'dun phal mo che la sngon ston pas 'og
NG0859:7831: min la sogs par gsang sngags kyi theg pa bstan
NG0859:7832: pa rnams slar yang bzlas te ston par mdzad la
NG0859:7833: / de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis
NG0859:7834: gser gyi glegs bam la baidur+ya zhun mas yi ger
NG0859:7835: bris te dgongs pa'i rtsal bdun gyis nam mkha' la
NG0859:7836: mi mngon par rgyas btab ste sbas so //
NG0859:7837: tshul 'di ni in+d+ra b+hu ti'i bde mchog rtsa rgyud
NG0859:7838: kyi 'grel pa'i lung gong du drangs pa bzhin no
NG0859:7839: // ri ma la ya yod pa'i lang+ka'i yul de
NG0859:7840: yang dzam+bu'i gling gi gling g.yog rnga yab kyi lang+ka
NG0859:7841: de ni ma yin te bcom ldan 'das lang+ka'i bdag

NG0859:7843: blo gros chen pos zhus pa las shin tu rgyas
NG0859:7844: pa chen po'i mdo lang kar gshegs pa gsungs pa'i
NG0859:7845: gnas dzam+bu gling gi shar lho mtshams kyi rgya mtshos
NG0859:7846: bcad pa'i gling phran zhig yin la /
NG0859:7851: pa yi gu'i gling sogs gling phran de dag rnams
NG0859:7852: su snga phyi ci rigs par bstan pa dar bar
NG0859:7853: yod cing */ bye brag lang+ka'i yul de sngon srin po sgra sgrogs kyis bzung ba'i phyir @#//
NG0859:7854: de ltar grags la phyis srin po'i yul stongs nas
NG0859:7855: de dpon seng ges bzung bas deng sang sing+ga la'i
NG0859:7856: gling du 'bod pa yin cing yul der slob dpon
NG0859:7857: chen po kah+na pa byon nas bi shwa ru bi
NG0859:7858: zhes pa'i srin mo chen mo 'khor lnga brgya'i tshogs
NG0859:7859: dang bcas pa btul ba dang */
NG0859:7860: sngags kyi bstan pa spel pa sogs mdzad /
NG0859:7861: phyis su theg chen gyi slob dpon lang+ka rgyal ba bzang po 'khrungs la /
NG0859:7862: slob dpon tsan+d+ra go mis kyang yul der byon /
NG0859:7863: shan+ti pa dang pan chen nags kyi rin chen yang
NG0859:7864: byan nas sngags kyi bstan pa spel ba sogs mdzad
NG0859:7865: cing sngon ma'i rgyal por ma nas mgrin bcu 'joms
NG0859:7866: pa'i dus dzam+bu'i gling dang de gnyis kyi bar rgya
NG0859:7867: mtsho chen po la rdo'i zam pa btsugs nas phyin
NG0859:7868: pas da ltar rgya mtsho'i nang du rdo'i phung po
NG0859:7869: chen po mngon sum du snang zhing skabs 'gar rdo'i
NG0859:7870: phung po la gzings thogs pas byol nas 'gro dgos
NG0859:7871: pa dang der srin po mgrin bcu bsad pa'i khrag
NG0859:7872: gis spags pa yin zer ba'i rdo dmar po kho

NG0859:10448: gnas gyur pa la gnyis 'dzin med //

NG0859:10450: sems had de ba la shes pa bkra gsal ba zhig byung */
NG0859:10451: kha nang na chu khyil le snang */
NG0859:10452: de ni dam pas byin gyis brlabs /
NG0859:10453: rdo rje zam pa dang mjal ba'i lung bstan par 'dug ste /
NG0859:10454: dus phyis las ma go gsungs /
NG0859:10456: sngags kyi gnad mang du gnang */
NG0859:10457: rgyang ru tshal mar yi ge drug pa'i gdams ngag gnang nas bsgrub pas byin rlabs chen po byung */
NG0859:10458: yang chu bo chen po 'di'i shar phyogs na tsan dan gyi nags yod /
NG0859:10459: de na khyod kyi bla ma yod gsungs nas lung bstan /
NG0859:10461: a khu dpal 'bal la khrag 'thung dang be har /
NG0859:10462: gnubs shangs po che la kr-i ya dang kha 'bar ma'i gtor chen zhus /
NG0859:10463: khong gis gtsang du ba ri ba la 'bul ba skyel du btang bas /
NG0859:10464: ba ri la'ang 'jam dpal dang khyung sgrub zhus /
NG0859:10465: dge bshes spo la snga 'gyur rigs zhus /
NG0859:10466: de nas sum cu rtsa lnga lon pa'i tshe ngam shod rgyud lcang tshigs su byon /
NG0859:10467: phug po che'i la kha na dge bshes btsan kha
NG0859:10468: bo che rgya gar nas byon ma thag pa gcig
NG0859:10469: jo mo bas spyan drangs nas /
NG0859:10470: chos dang bza' ba dang ltas mo yod zer /
NG0859:10471: nang par snga bar byon tsa na /
NG0859:10473: khrab nas lam zur 'di nas yar phyin na /
NG0859:10474: slob dpon sba sgom bya ba lto ster ba la yangs pa zhig yod zer /
NG0859:10475: phyin pas rnal 'byor pa tsho gcig gis kyang sleb nas tsha ba drangs /
NG0859:10476: phye zangs kyi khyem bu re yang gtong gi 'dug / de tshor byin zin nas /
NG0859:10477: de na gsar bu gcig kyang 'dug gsungs nas chu
NG0859:10478: bum pa gang len du bcug / chu gtor mdzad
NG0859:10479: nas phug chung zu rar khrid /
NG0859:10480: tshod ma ge ru pho pa gang byin /
NG0859:10481: de nub kyang bza' byin nas brag rtsa gcig tu nyal /
NG0859:10482: nang par 'gro dgos sems tsa na /
NG0859:10483: yang lto byin nas nga'i nye gnas btsun chung gcig
NG0859:10484: yod pa zo thang du gser len du song ba
NG0859:10487: der nags khrod nas shing khur che ba gcig bskyal bas /
NG0859:10488: sba sgom mnyes nas phyag rgya chen po brda'i man ngag dang */
NG0859:10489: rdzogs pa chen po skor bdun rang chas bya ba bshad /
NG0859:10491: nged ma sleb pas slob dpon 'og brgyal sems tsa
NG0859:10492: na khyed kyi go bcad 'dug pa da dung zhag
NG0859:10494: yang yar klung lan cig bskor nas byung */
NG0859:10495: der sba sgom gang zag khyad par can du shes
NG0859:10496: nas yul du ma phyin par 'on dang zangs ri
NG0859:10497: yan chad du bsod snyoms byas /
NG0859:10499: nas sgye gang dang bcas pa slob dpon sba sgom la phul bas /
NG0859:10500: khyod kyis nga'i g.yog byas pa yin pas des rung */
NG0859:10501: 'di la khyod rang gi rgyags gyis /
NG0859:10502: nga la man ngag rdo rje zam pa zhes bya
NG0859:10503: ba skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig lus
NG0859:10504: gcig la phung po lhag med du sangs rgyas pa'i
NG0859:10505: brgyud pa breng ma chad pa gcig yod /
NG0859:10506: da gong phan chad su la'ang ma smras pa yin /
NG0859:10507: da khyod la sbyin no gsungs /
NG0859:10508: nas nan gyis phul nas 'di slob dpon rang la bsngos pa yin /
NG0859:10509: gdams ngag thugs la gdags par zhu /
NG0859:10511: phyag g.yon pas sbyi bo nas bzung g.yas pas ltag khung nas rtab rtab byed cing */
NG0859:10512: 'or che dam tshig can du 'dug / gdams ngag gis phan thog par gda' gsungs /
NG0859:10513: der lo chung gi sngags pa gcig la gshin rje dmar po'i sgrub thabs zhig byin pas /
NG0859:10515: lo mo dang 'phrun du bsrung skyob zhar re tsam byas pa chos rgyags ldang ba rnyed /
NG0859:10516: der rdo rje zam pa'i byin rlabs zhu ba la tshogs kyi yo byad ma tshogs pa'i ngang */
NG0859:10520: gangs par du grogs po gcig la pir mo gcig bcol ba'i rin slong du phyin pas /
NG0859:10521: ma jo'i sham thabs zhig thob /
NG0859:10522: de'i snam pa tsho phral nas btsongs /
NG0859:10525: nas bre lnga sha gzugs gcig rnams la bsten nas /
NG0859:10526: mar me'i dod nyin par bya'o gsungs nas grol lam dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur /
NG0859:10527: gdams ngag ma lus pa gnang /
NG0859:10528: phyi nas kyang byin brlabs lan bzhi tsam zhus /
NG0859:10529: nas dang gser la sogs pa'i 'bul ba lan lnga bskyal /
NG0859:10531: snang ba 'di kun rdzun pa'i chos can yin gsungs nas /
NG0859:10532: chu rdo gcig la phyag char gyis brgyab pas grub mo yan chad thim gyis song */
NG0859:10533: yang sku lus phyir shigs kyi mdzad pas brag la 'dal gyis thal nas rjes wal le byung */
NG0859:10534: phug chung rong nas lta stangs kyis shug pa'i gdung
NG0859:10535: mang po bkug / jo mo'i mchod khang phug pa'i
NG0859:10536: shing yin gsungs / de lta bu'i slob dpon las
NG0859:10537: rdo rje zam pa'i skor ma lus pa thob cing
NG0859:10538: gzhan yang jo bo rje'i pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NG0859:10539: lam brkyang khug sogs kyang thob /
NG0859:10540: de bzhin du yu mo la sbyor drug / khams pa lung pa la thun brgyad ma /
NG0859:10542: slob ma la dmigs pa skor gsum /
NG0859:10543: shod bu lo tswa ba la 'grel chung */
NG0859:10544: dge bshes dgrol sgom la na ro'i thabs lam zhus shing */
NG0859:10545: rdo rje zam pa phar la bshad /
NG0859:10546: so snyun gdangs la sgron sprul dang rgyab sha / rdza bor ba la bdud rtsi thigs gsum /
NG0859:10547: ri khrod rlung chung la rna brgyud tshig gsum /
NG0859:10548: rlung ngam chen po la do ha'i man ngag / lab sgron la gcod yul /
NG0859:10549: rgyal ba sbo ston la sde skor bdun pa /
NG0859:10550: gnubs shangs chen la ba ri pa'i kr-i la'i chos bco lnga /
NG0859:10551: ding ri kun dga' la gdams pa sna tshogs sogs thos pa shin tu mang */
NG0859:10552: dwags po lha rje la chos drug dang skyes sbyor zhus /
NG0859:10553: rtogs pa nyams bsdur bas shin tu mnyes /
NG0859:10554: spyan snga rnal 'byor gyi gra sa ru spyod pa byas pas brtul zhugs can du grags /
NG0859:10555: grogs mched kyang a tsa ra stag sham can dang */
NG0859:10559: zhang 'gro smyon la sogs de tsa na'i rnal 'byor gyi dbang po sha stag dang 'grogs /
NG0859:10560: gtsang du gcer bu lo lnga byas /
NG0859:10561: gzhan yang snang ba la thog rdzis shin tu che bas dgun 'khyags pa'i rum /
NG0859:10563: ma nges pa'i g.yang rong zab mor mchong ba dang */
NG0859:10565: mtshon brdeg pa la sogs te spyod pa tshan po
NG0859:10566: che ma byas bya ba med pas dpa' bo 'dzeng
NG0859:10567: chung du grags / so mang btsan la phyag rgya
NG0859:10568: chen po btab pas 'khrul snang ye shes su gnas
NG0859:10569: chung du grags / gyur / ri khrod rlung chung pa dang */
NG0859:10570: dngul mo rgya le lcam la yi ge bzhi pa
NG0859:10571: dang rdzogs chen btab pas 'khrul zhig chen por gyur
NG0859:10572: te mthar phung po lhag med du dengs /
NG0859:10573: de bzhin du ma jo dad pa can dang */
NG0859:10574: khams pa snying rus can zhig la rdo rje zam
NG0859:10575: pa bstan pas ma jo mon kha zer mo'i mtsho
NG0859:10576: dang */ khams pa kong po mtsho rdzong du nam
NG0859:10577: mkha' dang mkha' 'gro'i 'chi lugs kyis phung po lhag
NG0859:10578: dang */ med du song */ ras pa sgom stag sho ras /
NG0859:10580: rlung ras sogs la gdams pa btab pa tsam gyis bde drod 'bar /
NG0859:10581: de bzhin du chos nyid bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs grol du song ba shin tu mang */
NG0859:10582: 'dzeng d+harma bo d+hi nyid kyis gsungs nas kyang */
NG0859:10583: nga'i gam du lo tsa ba yang bzhi tsam byung */
NG0859:10586: sgom pa sgom ma yus po che rang mthong can mang zhig byung */
NG0859:10587: tshul bzhin nyams su len pa a cang che ste /
NG0859:10588: dwags por nyams len en re byed pa'i nya ma bcu gcig tsam dang por 'chi dus thebs pa /
NG0859:10590: ro la 'ja' zug pa byung ba yin /
NG0859:10591: nga'i gdams pa 'di la bal ma bal las byed pa dang */
NG0859:10592: pha ma sri'u gso ba 'dra ba'i nyams len lo lnga drug gcig byas na /
NG0859:10593: phung po lhag med du song nas shul du mi'i lus po mi yong nges gsungs /
NG0859:10594: rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pa rgya mtsho lta bu la dbang 'byor bas re sku lus 'ja' ru 'khyil /
NG0859:10595: res zhabs sa la mi reg par gshegs /
NG0859:10597: gcig tu 'dres pas thag ring po'i sa yang yud tsam la 'khor /
NG0859:10598: gzhan sems shes pa la sogs pa'i mngon par shes
NG0859:10599: pa thogs med mnga' bas ma 'ongs pa thams cad
NG0859:10600: lung ston / lha'i mig dag pas jo sras ma
NG0859:10601: rdo rje skyid kyi bu nam phyed na gnyid log
NG0859:10602: pa rgya mthongs nas mar rbab tu 'chor la khad
NG0859:10603: lung ston / pa gzigs / snang ba la nyin
NG0859:10604: mtshan med pas nub mo sbur ma'i khrod du rgya
NG0859:10605: khab ltung ba bde blag tu gzigs pa sogs yod
NG0859:10606: lung ston / pa gzigs / / phyi res gtsang
NG0859:10607: du lo bdun bzhugs nas slar phug po cher byon
NG0859:10608: lung ston / pa gzigs / / pas / slob dpon sba sgom gyis /
NG0859:10609: nam mkha' 'di khong du chud par gyis /
NG0859:10610: de rten med du rtogs nas sgom med kyi gzar
NG0859:10611: chen thebs pa yin gsungs pas nges shes gting nas
NG0859:10612: 'drongs / de nas dwags po zhu ru bzhugs shing
NG0859:10613: bla ma zhal gdams la gu ru zhi ba sde
NG0859:10614: skor mdun pa'i gdams pa zhus /
NG0859:10615: de'i lta zur dgon par brda' bzhi lo gsum bskyangs pas chos thams cad la byan tshud /
NG0859:10616: spros bral gyi dgongs pa nam mkha' lta bur song */
NG0859:10617: lar dka' thub la shin tu bzod pas /
NG0859:10618: phug po cher rdo rje zam pa zhus nas bdud rtsi'i dka' thub mdzad /
NG0859:10619: rims kyis rdzi bar ma nus /
NG0859:10620: gnubs shong po che'i drung du bla ma'i bran gyi
NG0859:10621: dka' thub byas par gar phyin du bla mas thugs
NG0859:10622: la 'dogs / dam pa rgya gar gyi drung du
NG0859:10623: rtog dpyod kyi dka' thub byas pas chos thams cad
NG0859:10625: skyid khung du phur pa'i bzlas pa la dka' thub
NG0859:10626: byas pas 'jig rten gyi lha 'dres ci smras nyan
NG0859:10627: / jo bo bka' gdams pa'i sa ru zhi dul
NG0859:10628: gyi dka' thub byas pas gar phyin du gzhan gyis
NG0859:10629: / byams / yi ge bzhi la mi sdod pa
NG0859:10630: gsum gyi dka' thub byas pa bde drod 'bar nas
NG0859:10632: de la nges shes skyes nas phag mo mngon 'byung
NG0859:10633: la sgrub pa'i dka' thub byas pas 'gur mo'i nub
NG0859:10634: phyogs su rje btsun mi'i zhal gzigs /
NG0859:10636: gnubs yul rong du rmi lam sbyangs pas snang ba thams cad rmi lam du shes /
NG0859:10637: gzho stod ti sgro'i shel phug tu khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i zhal mthong */
NG0859:10638: mi ma yin cig gis bsnyen bkur cher byas /
NG0859:10639: btsun gzugs gcig nam mkha' la 'phur nas phar 'gro tshur 'gro byed pa mthong */
NG0859:10640: btsal bas ma rnyed mi yin min ma shes gsungs /
NG0859:10641: dwags po zhu ru a dzi bsgrubs pas nyi ma dro khar zhal gzigs /
NG0859:10642: dam bsre byed snyam tsa na jo mo phya le byon nas /
NG0859:10643: bud med can zer nas 'od cig tu yal /
NG0859:10644: lha zur du bcud len gyi sgrub pa byas pa tshe dpag med zhal mthong */
NG0859:10645: chos mang po'i rnam gzhag rgyud la shar /
NG0859:10646: o dkar brag tu sgrub pa mdzad pas bde mchog yab yum zhal gzigs /
NG0859:10647: lan cig 'gro snying 'dod pa zhig byung nas /
NG0859:10648: mor 'gar grong mo che'i mdun du byon /
NG0859:10649: chu'i rdzing mo zhig la thub chod byas mchongs pas /
NG0859:10653: chu la rlangs pa nam mkha' mi mthong ba tsam byung */
NG0859:10654: mi rnams ngo mtshar skyes nas dgun grang bdo ba la de tsam tshugs pa /
NG0859:10655: lcags bsregs chu la btsud pa 'dra ba byung zer /
NG0859:10656: rang la 'khyags pa'i snang ba ni byung gsungs /
NG0859:10657: yang lan cig jo mo dang gnyis kyis shing 'thur phyin pas shing khur che ba gcig rnyed /
NG0859:10658: de khur nas mtha' chen po gcig gi khar sleb pa dang */
NG0859:10659: 'di ni rmi lam du 'dug snyam nas mchongs pas bya babs pa bzhin du song */
NG0859:10660: jo mo na re bla ma khyed mi'ang cig mi 'dug / dam pa rgya gar dran zer /
NG0859:10661: de yan du gdams pa mang du ma 'phel /
NG0859:10662: grong chog mdzad cing gsang spyod bskyangs /
NG0859:10663: de nas thag ring nas slob ma mang du byung nas 'phel /
NG0859:10664: re zhig na bal bu dor las spyan drangs /
NG0859:10666: nyi ma snga dro dang po la 'ja'i gdugs dang re mig mang po byung */
NG0859:10667: chos thon nas ri logs la skyo sangs la byon /
NG0859:10668: 'ja' de bla ma grongs pa'i rtags mi dga' ba min nam zhus pas /
NG0859:10669: nga'i bla ma sba sgom gyis 'bar ston shes rab
NG0859:10670: grags spun gnyis la gdams pa 'di gnang ba'i dus
NG0859:10671: kyang */ ngams shod lung pa dang */
NG0859:10672: phug po che'i ri logs khengs pa tsam byung ba yin /
NG0859:10674: yang bla ma 'di 'dzin na bzhugs pa'i dus su
NG0859:10675: slob ma jo sras 'dzeng gi drung du byon pas
NG0859:10676: / mchod rten rtsa ba'i gad rtsa gcig na bzhugs
NG0859:10677: 'dug / de nas dben khang du phyin tsa na
NG0859:10679: 'od phub tsam zhig 'dug / rtsar nya tsa na
NG0859:10680: 'od de mi 'dug nas de tsug lags zhus pas
NG0859:10681: / mnyam par bzhag pa'i rtags yin mi la ma smra gsungs /
NG0859:10682: yang a jo dngos grub la mdze byung bas /
NG0859:10683: ngas bzlas grogs byas mdze ni ma sos /
NG0859:10684: ngas phyag na rdo rje'i zhal mthong dgod bro gsungs /
NG0859:10685: de ltar chos tshul gzhan la grags pa'i ro snyoms dang */
NG0859:10688: rim pa lnga la sogs pa'i gdams pa'i don gyi
NG0859:10689: thob bya gang yin pa nyams 'og tu chud pa'i
NG0859:10690: 'dzeng sgom d+harma bo d+hi 'di dgung lo brgya dang
NG0859:10691: gnyis lon pa'i dus zhig snyun pa ltar bstan pas
NG0859:10692: / 'khor rnams kyis bla ma grongs kyi dogs tsa na /
NG0859:10693: zhal nas mdang rmi lam bzang */
NG0859:10694: nga mi 'chi rgya'i po ra'i steng na 'dug pa la nyi zla gnyis shar byung */
NG0859:10695: rus pa'i spyil po mang po'i steng na bud med mang po 'dug pas /
NG0859:10696: bla ma 'dzeng khyod lo bzhi na shog zer ba gcig rmis gsungs /
NG0859:10698: ngas lo mang po lon te nga la'ang tig pa bshad rgyu med gsungs /
NG0859:10699: de ni rtog dpyod la 'dzin pa dag pas nang
NG0859:10700: du dgongs pa zad sar 'khyol ba'i rtags yin no
NG0859:10701: // der 'khor rnams kyis dge rtsa gcig mdzad par zhus pas /
NG0859:10702: 'dus byas kyi dge rtsa la thugs mi gtod /
NG0859:10703: bcud len cig mdzad par zhus pas kyang */
NG0859:10704: bcud len byas na lo bcu tsam
NG0859:10707: dus ngan gyi tshe ring ba la dgos pa med gsungs /
NG0859:10708: gzhan la skyo ba yang dag bskul nas sku gshegs so //
NG0859:10709: pur sbyangs pas nam mkha' 'jas gang */
NG0859:10710: mchod rten dang ring bsrel yang mang du byon don /
NG0859:10711: 'di ni tshogs pa bskyangs pas snyigs ma 'ja' lus su ma dengs kyang */
NG0859:10712: don gyi ka dag chos zad kyi sa la mya
NG0859:10713: ngan las 'das pa'i rtags mtha' dag tshang zhing snyan
NG0859:10714: brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i dar rgyas kyang 'di'i ring
NG0859:10715: nas che bar byung ste dngos kyi slob ma yang
NG0859:10718: btsan thang pa nyang d+harma sid+ha dang */
NG0859:10719: slob dpon gser lung pa dang */
NG0859:10720: bla ma du rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang */
NG0859:10721: gzig ye shes dbang po dang */
NG0859:10722: g.yag ston zla ba 'od zer la sogs mang du byon no //
NG0859:10723: dgung lo yang brgya dang bcu bdun lon tshe gshegs pa yin /
NG0859:10725: phya pa chos kyi seng ge dang */
NG0859:10726: rje btsun mi la dpon slob dang snga phyir thog mnyam pa tsam yin no //
NG0859:10728: sngags pa'i rigs la btsas pas chung ngu nas yig rtses la sbyangs /
NG0859:10729: 'ol kha'i lha bris pa la sgyu 'phrul la sogs rnying ma dang */
NG0859:10730: dgyes rdor dang mtshan brjod zhus /
NG0859:10731: slob dpon lha ris pa 'da' khar gzhung chen po
NG0859:10732: 'di tsam zhig shes kyang 'chi khar pa a ro
NG0859:10734: khyod rang kyang gzhung ma bslabs par gdams ngag la nan tan gyis /
NG0859:10735: dwags po na khyed rang gi bla ma 'dzeng bya
NG0859:10736: ba gcig yod 'dug pas der song zhes lung bstan
NG0859:10737: / gang bar du rdzogs chen lhun grub mkhan slob
NG0859:10738: dpon zem gyi sar dbyar dgun thog drug bsdad kyang
NG0859:10740: gdams ngag gi spros pa ma chod nas slob dpon
NG0859:10741: 'dzeng la dpal lung du rdo rje zam pa tshar
NG0859:10742: gsum zhus / byin rlabs mdzad nas /
NG0859:10743: khyed rang re zhig gtsang du song la gzhung slob /
NG0859:10744: gtsang nas 'khor tsa na a mis dgon pa gcig tu sdod cig gsungs /
NG0859:10745: der gdams pa mi gnang ba dgongs nas /
NG0859:10747: gra phyi'i jo sras zhang la skyabs bya bas shes gsungs /
NG0859:10748: de la zhu bar sems tsa na khong grongs /
NG0859:10749: yang dwags po rang du log nas 'dzeng la zhus pas kyang ma gnang */
NG0859:10750: slob ma gcig la zhu bsams nas /
NG0859:10751: sho skyam du slob dpon ngu'i spyan sngar phyin tsa na /
NG0859:10752: re ba tsam bcos nas 'dis mi 'ongs da dung dwags por song la zhus gsungs /
NG0859:10753: yang dwags por byon nas zhus pas /
NG0859:10754: cis kyang 'dod na gdams pa la nan tan byed dgos pa yin gsungs nas rdzogs par gnang */
NG0859:10755: dbyar dgun thog 'ga' slob dpon gyi drung du bsdad /
NG0859:10756: lo drug tsam lon nas phran tshegs rnams kyang rdzogs /
NG0859:10757: gzhan la byin rlab mdzad pa'i las slob kyang byas /
NG0859:10758: thod pa'i slob ma rog po dga' dang */
NG0859:10759: ma jo bzlo ba la sogs pa lnga bcu tsam gyis rdo rje @#//
NG0859:10760: zam pa zhus pas jo sras kyis shod /
NG0859:10761: khyed tshos nyon gsungs nas slob dpon gyi khri kha nas gsungs /
NG0859:10762: dpon slob gnyis lo ngo bco brgyad tsam du 'grogs /
NG0859:10763: gdams ngag gi bka' phog nas brgyud 'dzin bskos so //
NG0859:10764: de ltar 'dzeng d+harma bo d+hi dang */
NG0859:10765: jo sras 'dzeng chung smyon pa gnyi ga'i slob ma slob dpon kun bzang yin te /
NG0859:10766: de ni khu bo pha jo dbus pa phag mo gru pa'i slob ma sgom chen po zhig yin /
NG0859:10767: ma zi bza' des chog bya ba ma jo smyon
NG0859:10768: ma bsam 'grub bya ba la chos thob pa gnyis
NG0859:10769: ka la rmi lam gyi ltas bzang po dang bcas
NG0859:10770: te 'khrungs / lo brgyad dgu la slob dpon kor ston ra dza las slob gnyer cung zad byas /
NG0859:10771: bco lnga lon pa'i tshe khong grongs nas slob dpon
NG0859:10772: du ba'i gam du lo lnga tsam zhi byed zhu

NG0859:13186: [(]16[)]@#// rwa dbrag tu zur po che dpal chen po'i skur

NG0859:14092: rtse phron byang dpal dang brgyad do //

NG0859:14107: mgo chung dbang nge gsum mo //

NG0859:14115: sku la snyun pa mi mnga' 'am snyam nas nye gnas kyis bltar phyin tsa na /

NG0859:14119: la bzhag na mgo la thod pa mi 'gel ba
NG0859:14121: da skye ba gcig len par 'dug gsungs /

NG0859:14125: yang nang gcig / tsha ba'i sta gon gyis shig / da res lo ma'i tshod ma bya'o gsungs /
NG0859:14126: nye gnas kyis chu ma khol ba la bla mas tshod ma bsnams byung */
NG0859:14127: ngas 'ug pa lung 'khor nas khyod chu mi khol ba ci yin gsungs /

NG0859:14135: mig chung dbang seng na re /
NG0859:14136: dkyil 'khor phyir 'don pa la rgyab tu yo ga

NG0859:14138: */ 'gos chung dbang nges bzhi lam gyi grub mtha'i

NG0859:14142: grol gnyis ka yod de ma rgyud kyi mtshan nyid

NG0859:14144: tshad ma tshig gi grub mtha' yin te gzhi lam

NG0859:14149: sgro phug lha khang gi mjug skyongs dang */

NG0859:14175: kho'i drung du phyin tsa na bcom ldan 'das dpal @#//

NG0859:14189: bka' srung legs ldan lde gur bzhengs /

NG0859:14208: lha rje zur chung pa de sku mya ngan las

NG0859:15076: 'dun la phul / tu mkhas / rgod sgros chu'i
NG0859:15077: grod pa dum bur bcad kyang chu mi 'bo ba
NG0859:15078: 'dun la phul / tu mkhas / dang */ lcags
NG0859:15079: bsregs la sha rjen gyis reg kyang mi 'tshig pa
NG0859:15081: rtsigs pa la rdo drug sbyor gyi zhal ba byas
NG0859:15082: pa rtsigs pa brag chen la 'gyur ba la sogs
NG0859:15084: gtso bor karma pa rang byung rdo rje'i dbugs 'byin
NG0859:15085: chen pos man ngag spyi dang khyad par rdzogs pa
NG0859:15086: chen po la nyams bzhes mdzad /
NG0859:15087: rgya cher rol pa las bshad pa'i gter chen po brgyad thob pas /
NG0859:15088: legs par bshad pas sems can thams cad tshim par
NG0859:15089: byed pa spobs pa'i gter chen po yongs su grol
NG0859:15090: nas / mdo sngags kyi sangs rgyas la khyad par
NG0859:15091: phye ba'i bstan bcos mdzad pa g.yag sde pan chen
NG0859:15092: nas / gyis gzigs / shin tu dad pas dpon slob bco lngas byon te zhabs la gtugs //
NG0859:15093: sku tshe'i smad la tshogs pa chos lung pa las bsnyen par rdzogs /
NG0859:15094: mtshan rdo rje 'bum zhes pa rdo rje dpal du bsgyur /  mon spa gro dang */
NG0859:15096: ra dum brag la sogs par bzhugs shing bshad pas kyang gzhan la phan pa rgya chen po mdzad /
NG0859:15097: brgyad cu rtsa gnyis pa shing mo sprul gyi lor zhi bar gshegs so ///
NG0859:15098: / rta nag sgrol ma ba bsam 'grub rdo rje ni /
NG0859:15099: sngags rnying ma las dngos grub brnyes pa rim can gyi sras su rta nag gnas gsar du 'khrungs /
NG0859:15100: zur byams pa seng ge las gsan pa rgya chen
NG0859:15101: po mdzad cing khyad par sgyu 'phrul la mchog tu
NG0859:15102: mkhas / glan nya tshal pa bsod nams mgon po la sgyu 'phrul gyi dbang nod /
NG0859:15103: mkhyen pa dang phrin las dpag par dka' ba yin te dben pa 'ba' zhig la thugs gtad do //
NG0859:15104: bye ma seng ger rdzogs pa chen po snying thig la thugs dam rtse gcig tu mdzad /
NG0859:15106: phebs te sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa de nyid du spyod /
NG0859:15107: yang dben pa'i zur shakya 'byung gnas dang */
NG0859:15108: 'ug pa lung pa'i bla ma seng ge pa gnyis
NG0859:15109: chung chung nas sku drung du bzhag na legs pas
NG0859:15110: bskyangs pa'i bla ma'i dam tshig la gcig tu gus
NG0859:15111: shing */ zur rgyud la bka' drin che /
NG0859:15112: shangs pa kun mkhyen zhes grags pa bla na gsal
NG0859:15113: ba de'ang byis pa'i dus na bla ma 'dis dbang
NG0859:15114: mang po bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pas mkhas pa
NG0859:15115: chen por gyur pa sogs byin rlab bsam gyis mi
NG0859:15116: khyab / dgung lo brgyad cu rtsa gnyis pa me pho 'brug gi lo gshegs khar sras la /
NG0859:15118: khyed kyis kyang nga'i lo dang mnyam pa thub /
NG0859:15119: de nas bde ba can du shog ces gsungs nas gshegs /
NG0859:15121: sras rgyud gnyis las zur rgyud ni /
NG0859:15123: 'di'i yab zur bzang po dpal zhes bya ba'i ring
NG0859:15124: la gong ma bu yan thu gan gyi lung dang
NG0859:15125: gnang byin blangs / slar gong ma'i lung gis rgya nag ru 'byon dgos pa byung */
NG0859:15126: dang po gong ma rgyal po'i rim gro par gyur
NG0859:15127: la mthu rtsal dang nus pa shin tu che bas
NG0859:15128: lo nyes las skyobs pa dang */
NG0859:15129: mdos zor thog sel la sogs pas ngo log choms nus /
NG0859:15130: khyad par rgyal po'i pho brang ta'i tu'i steng gi
NG0859:15131: nam mkhar mi mthun pa'i mtshan ma sprin nag po
NG0859:15132: sdig pa'i gzugs can byung ba sus kyang bshig ma
NG0859:15133: nus pa'i tshe / rgyal po'i lung gis skabs dbye
NG0859:15134: nas ma mo 'khang phab kyi mdos dar khang bco
NG0859:15136: gtor 'chams mdzad pas sprin nag 'thor ba sogs mtha'
NG0859:15137: 'khob gyi yul du dam pa'i chos kyi che ba
NG0859:15138: lan mang du bton pas gong ma dad de /
NG0859:15139: yang dag lha dgu'i dbang dang tshe dbang zhus /
NG0859:15142: phod kha phyed gnyis brgya 'dengs pa'i gos dar gyi 'bul ba phul /
NG0859:15143: pho brang ta'i tur sngags sde btsugs /
NG0859:15144: de'i dus kyi las bzhi'i phur pa pho brang na yod par grags /
NG0859:15145: de ltar zang zing gi rdzas 'byor pa las rtsa rgyud gsang snying */
NG0859:15148: man ngag dgu pa sogs pa'i snga 'gyur gyi chos sde nyi shu rtsa brgyad par du bsgrubs /
NG0859:15149: so so nas stong phrag re btab ste grwa pa la bkye /
NG0859:15150: rgyud 'bum bzhengs pa'i cha rkyen mang po bskur ba sogs bstan pa la phan pa rgya che /
NG0859:15151: slar rgyal po bu yan thu rlung gi nad la tshad pa'i bcos byas nas gshegs //
NG0859:15152: 'di dus sa skya dang zur tsho rnams grub mtha'i
NG0859:15153: snying po gcig pas 'dris shin tu zab pa yin
NG0859:15154: / rgyu des zur byams pa seng ge gshegs pa'i lo rgyus sa skyar bskyal bas /
NG0859:15156: da zur bzang po dpal rgya nag nas bos shig gsungs /
NG0859:15157: gzhan rnams kyang bgros nas nye gnas 'jam dbyangs gdan 'dren du btang */
NG0859:15158: des rgya nag tu brtol ba'i tshe tshad pa'i nad kyis bsnyun @#//
NG0859:15160: mkha' 'gro chos skyong gi byin gyis brlabs nas cung drag pa'i mgo bstan /
NG0859:15161: de'i tshe nyid kyi gzigs snang la rgyal po bu yan thu dang mjal nas /
NG0859:15162: khyod bod du 'byon nam gnang sbyin ji ltar byin ces gsungs pa la lan zhib tu zhus pas /
NG0859:15163: ci yang ma byin par 'dug gsungs nas yal /
NG0859:15164: de'i lo rgyus dpon mo tha bu las thos te
NG0859:15165: khyod mthong bas gong ma dran zer nas mchi ma
NG0859:15166: phyung */ slar dngul bre bcu byin /
NG0859:15167: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku rgya nag li ma dang */
NG0859:15168: chos skyong lcam bral gyi 'chams sku bzhengs pa gdan
NG0859:15169: drangs nas bod la byon pa'i tshe mgon pos bod
NG0859:15170: la zhal gzigs nas gom pa bdun 'phags pas bse
NG0859:15172: bod du byon nas bstan pa'i bya ba la rgyud 'bum bzhengs /
NG0859:15174: ma 'ongs pa mngon sum du lung ston /
NG0859:15175: slar yang gong ma'i lung gis rgya nag tu gshegs dgos pa byung ba'i tshe /
NG0859:15177: rgyal po'i pho nya the mur dar dang */
NG0859:15178: g+ha ra la dngul bre la sogs pa byin te
NG0859:15179: slog kyang rgyal po'i chad pa 'ong zer 'gro ma
NG0859:15180: 'dod / der rang dbang thams cad bde ba yin /
NG0859:15181: gzhan dbang thams cad sdug bsngal yin /
NG0859:15182: zhes pa la sogs pa'i zhal gdams mdzad nas rgya nag tu gshegs /
NG0859:15183: spyir dgung lo sum cu so brgyad las ma bzhugs pa de'i sras yin /
NG0859:15184: de la zur ham shaka 'byung 'dis chung ngu nas
NG0859:15185: yab mes kyi chos la sbyangs shing las sad pas
NG0859:15186: / rang lo lnga par yab rgya yul du gshegs
NG0859:15187: pa'i bsu ba mi chen dang bcas pa'i dbus su
NG0859:15188: rtsa rgyud la bshad pa tho re long mdzad pa
NG0859:15190: dgung lo bdun pa nas bshad grwa bskyangs /
NG0859:15191: bla ma kun spangs sar dge tshul dang */
NG0859:15192: chos rje bsod nams grags pa las bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mtshan shakya 'byung gnas su grags /
NG0859:15194: zur shakya seng ge zhes bya ba go lug rgyal po'i lung dang */
NG0859:15195: gnang byin gser bre chen srang drug cu ma bzhi /
NG0859:15196: dngul dgar bre chen nyi shu /
NG0859:15197: gos phyi nang nyis brgya rnams thob cing */
NG0859:15198: dpon mo tha'u sogs pas kyang bdog pa rgya cher
NG0859:15199: byin pas zur pa'i bstan srid la phan pa rgya
NG0859:15200: cher btags la / khyad par rgyal ba zur po
NG0859:15201: che'i sku chos kyi dum bu bzhugs pa'i 'jam dbyangs
NG0859:15202: kyi gser sku shin tu mtshar ba bzhengs nas dpal
NG0859:15203: 'ug bya lung gi rten gtsor mnga' gsol /
NG0859:15204: bshad grwa dang sgom grwa'i tshugs kha chen po zin par byas /
NG0859:15205: bdog pa la 'phangs pa med pas bstan pa'i rim gro lhur len /
NG0859:15206: mthong na mi mthun pa med pa'i gzi byin gyis
NG0859:15207: hor gyi mi chen the mur dar kyang dad par
NG0859:15208: gyur nas tshe dbang zhu ba la sogs pa'i dang
NG0859:15209: ba ston nus pa'i sems dpa' chen po'i ngang tshul
NG0859:15211: sa bzang lo chen rgyal ba g.yung */
NG0859:15215: dbu che grags pa che ba rnams kyis mtshon bod
NG0859:15216: dbus gtsang gi mkhas btsun bzang gsum thams cad la
NG0859:15217: gtugs nas mtshan nyid sde gsum /
NG0859:15218: gsang sngags gsar rnying thams cad kyi gzhung dang man ngag la legs par sbyangs /
NG0859:15219: khyad par du mngon rtogs rgyan /
NG0859:15224: 'grel pa spar khab rnams nan tan du sbyangs pas mkhas grub chen por grags /
NG0859:15225: dus phyis mdo dbang zur lugs kyi bstan pa'i bdag po 'di kho na yin /
NG0859:15226: sgrol chen bsam rdor las mdo dbang gsan pa'i tshe /
NG0859:15229: nas khal lnga bcu sogs kyis sna drangs pa'i 'bul
NG0859:15230: ba byas te lung lag len phyag bzhes thams cad
NG0859:15232: gtad rgya kho na'i don du'ang gos yug chen dang gser gyi 'bul bas mnyes par mdzad /
NG0859:15234: he ru ka rigs lnga gzigs snang du shin tu gsal ba gzigs /
NG0859:15236: gtad rgya'i 'grel pa sogs mang du mdzad /
NG0859:15237: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi bstan pa la bya ba rgya chen po mdzad cing */
NG0859:15238: sgrol ma pa'i sras sangs rgyas rin chen dang */
NG0859:15239: gnyal pa bde legs pa la sogs te bstan pa'i
NG0859:15240: gsal byed du gyur pa'i slob ma mang dag bskrun
NG0859:15241: nas dgung lo sum cu so brgyad la gshegs /
NG0859:15242: gnyal pa bde legs kyi chog khrigs kyang yod do ///
NG0859:15243: / yang sgrol chen pa'i sras pha rgyud ltar byas na /
NG0859:15244: sras sangs rgyas rin chen rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po
NG0859:15245: zhes grags pa de nyid yab kyi lnga bcu rtsa
NG0859:15246: drug pa lcags pho stag la gnas gsar du 'khrungs
NG0859:15247: / mi rnams kyis khyed kyi sras 'dis phan ni mi thogs /
NG0859:15248: de tsam gyi gtsigs kyis ci bya zer bas /
NG0859:15249: 'gro ba la phan thogs pa gcig 'ong gsungs /
NG0859:15250: dgung lo drug pa la gsang ba snying po'i rgyud thugs su tshud /
NG0859:15251: zur shaka 'byung ba'i spyan sngar byon /
NG0859:15252: nga'i bla ma'i sras zhes gces par bskyangs pas rgyud bzung ba de g.yengs /
NG0859:15253: yang lo brgyad lon pa na bskyar te bzung */
NG0859:15254: chos brin rnams yab kyis bslabs pas lo bcu bzhi
NG0859:15255: par gzhan la dbang skur ba'i slob dpon pher pa
NG0859:15256: byung */ yab las sgyu 'phrul gyi chos skor rnams thugs su chud par mdzad /
NG0859:15257: da nga rab tu byung nas mtshan nyid kyang sbyang */
NG0859:15258: gsar ma'i rgyud sde'ang slob pa yin zhus pas /
NG0859:15260: gzod rab tu byung bas chog gsungs /
NG0859:15261: der ma gcig zhig bdag gir bzung bas sras kha shas 'khrungs /
NG0859:15262: dge bsnyen gyi rten la bslab sbyangs rdzogs par mdzad /
NG0859:15263: slar chos 'khor sgang du chig rdzogs mdzad /
NG0859:15264: sku shin tu btsun par bzhugs /
NG0859:15265: sgyu 'phrul la mkhas par gyur pas dgung lo bzhi
NG0859:15266: bcu skor la gsang ba snying po la ti ka
NG0859:15268: lam rnam bkod la'ang rnam bshad chen po zhig mdzad /
NG0859:15269: de bzhin du phrin las shar @#//
NG0859:15271: khro bo la mngon par rtogs pa rgyas pa zhig mdzad pa dang */
NG0859:15272: gnas lung la'ang cho ga rgyas pa zhig mdzad /
NG0859:15273: yab dang thugs sras thub pa rdo rje sogs la man ngag mang du mnyan cing nyams su bstar /
NG0859:15274: dgung lo bcu bdun pa la 'gos lo ye bzang rtse ba rjes su bzung ste /
NG0859:15275: 'di ltar sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang dang */
NG0859:15279: yang dag me gcig gi dbang */
NG0859:15280: sna bo pa'i lugs kyi rta mgrin dang */
NG0859:15281: zla rgyal ma'i lugs kyi rjes gnang */
NG0859:15282: phur pa sa lugs kyi dbang drag po'i rjes gnang dang bcas pa /
NG0859:15283: sems sde bco brgyad kyi rig pa'i rtsal dbang */
NG0859:15284: gsang snying rgyud 'grel pa dang bcas pa'i bshad pa /
NG0859:15285: lam rnam par bkod pa'i ti ka gnyis kyis mdzad pa'i thog nas bshad pa rgyas pa /
NG0859:15286: gzhan sgyu 'phul gyi khog gzhung bzhi bcu la sogs pa'i gzhung chung bzhi bcu tsam /
NG0859:15288: de'i rtsa ba'i rgyud kun 'dus dang */
NG0859:15289: gnubs chen gyi mdo 'grel mun pa'i go cha /
NG0859:15292: yang dag rtsa ba'i lung rnams kyang gnang */
NG0859:15293: snying thig spros bcas la sogs pa'i dbang bzhi dang */
NG0859:15294: me long bas mdzad pa'i yi ge'i steng nas khrid
NG0859:15295: yig / rdzogs chen a ro'i man ngag kyang khrid
NG0859:15296: du mdzad / de bzhin du byang sems ye rgyal
NG0859:15297: ba nas brgyud pa'i thugs rje chen po'i smar khrid
NG0859:15298: du mdzad / kyang gnang ste / rgyu mtshan de la brten nas 'gos lo ye bzang rtse bas /
NG0859:15299: gsang sngags rnying ma zhes grags pa'i phyogs la lhag par mos pa thob cing */
NG0859:15300: chos spangs pa'i sgribs pas ma spags tsam mo //
NG0859:15301: zhes thos pa'i pha rol tu son pa'i mthar thug
NG0859:15302: don dang ldan par song ba yin zhes nges pa
NG0859:15303: brten pa'i tha tshig go / de ltar chos rje
NG0859:15304: sangs rgyas rin chen pas bdun bcu rtsa gnyis pa
NG0859:15305: lcags mo glang gi lo la dbus su phebs /
NG0859:15306: gangs po ri'i bsam gtan gling du dbang grags pa rgyal mtshan gyis zhabs nas btegs /
NG0859:15307: 'dus pa mdo la sogs pa'i dbang mang po dang */
NG0859:15308: gsang snying la sogs pa'i bshad pa dang lung mang po byin /
NG0859:15309: brgyad cu rtsa gnyis pa lcags mo phag gi lo la gtsang du sku gshegs /
NG0859:15310: zur chung pa 'khrungs gnas dus 'di yan chad la lo bzhi brgya dang bcu bdun song ///
NG0859:15311: / bdag nyid chen po 'gos gzhon nu dpal ni yab 'gos ston 'byung gnas rdo rje dang */
NG0859:15312: yum srid thar skyid gnyis kyi sras su chu sprel la 'khrungs /
NG0859:15313: spyan g.yas mkhan chen las rab tu byung */
NG0859:15314: karma pa de bzhin gshegs pa las byang sdom dang */
NG0859:15316: rngog byang chub dpal las rngog chos rnams gsan /
NG0859:15317: khyad par pan chen ba na rat+na las bla med
NG0859:15318: kyi rgyud sde phal mo che'i dbang bskur ba rnams
NG0859:15319: zhus / mtshan brjod dang dpyid thig / dbang mdor bstan /
NG0859:15320: dpe med 'tsho'i sbyor drug rtsa 'grel rnams zhus shing @#//
NG0859:15322: rje 'di nyid kyis sgrol chen sangs rgyas rin chen
NG0859:15323: dgung lo bdun cu pa la sa mo phag gi
NG0859:15324: lor sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang dang */
NG0859:15326: na rag dong sbrugs tshe bdag / yang dag me gcig rta mgrin /
NG0859:15327: lha mo dang zla rgyal lugs /
NG0859:15329: sems sde bco brgyad kyi rigs pa'i rtsal dbang sogs
NG0859:15330: snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i dbang bka' thams cad ma tshang
NG0859:15332: bshad pa'i bka' gsang ba snying po rgyud dang 'grel pa so sor bshad pa dang */
NG0859:15333: lam rnam bkod kyi ti ka khong nyid kyis mdzad pa dang */
NG0859:15334: gzhan yang khog gzhung gsal sgron sogs rgya bod kyi
NG0859:15335: gzhung chung bzhi bcu skor gyi bshad lung rnams dang
NG0859:15336: */ mdo dgongs 'dus dang de'i rtsa ba'i rgyud kun 'dus rig pa dang */
NG0859:15337: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis mdzad pa'i mdo'i 'grel pa mun pa'i go cha /
NG0859:15341: yang dag rtsa ba'i lung rnams kyang gsan /
NG0859:15342: snying thig la rtsa ba'i dbang spros bcas spros med bzhi'i dbang bskur ba dang */
NG0859:15343: grub thob me long rdo rjes mdzad pa'i khrid yig gi steng nas khrid dang */
NG0859:15344: a ro'i lugs kyi rdzogs chen man ngag gi khrid
NG0859:15345: kyang gsan zhing mdor na gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi
NG0859:15346: bstan pa'i bdag po lta bur gyur zhing rje nyid
NG0859:15347: kyis kyang gsang sngags rnying ma zhes grags pa'i phyogs
NG0859:15348: la lhag par mos pa thob cing */
NG0859:15349: chos spangs pa'i sgrib pas ma spags tsam mo //
NG0859:15350: zhes gsungs pa'ang bod kyi mkhas rlom phyogs lhung can 'ga' zhig la dgongs pa yin te /
NG0859:15351: don du'ang rje 'di ni grub mtha' phyogs su ma
NG0859:15352: lhung ba'i bshes gnyen gzhan las khyad par du 'phags
NG0859:15353: pa yin cing bstan bcos rnams kyang tshad mar gyur
NG0859:15354: pa'i legs bshad che ba yang mngon sum gyis grub
NG0859:15355: bo // rje 'dis karma pa chos grags rgya mtsho
NG0859:15356: la sems 'grel skor gsum sogs chos bka' dbang khrid
NG0859:15357: bo // mang po phul / zhwa dmar cod pan
NG0859:15358: 'dzin pa bzhi pa chos kyi grags pa ye shes
NG0859:15359: dpal bzang po bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mkhan po dang
NG0859:15360: sgru 'phrul gtso bor gyur pa'i gsar rnying gi rgyud
NG0859:15363: man ngag gi khrid sogs bsam gyis mi khyab par gnang */
NG0859:15364: rje zhwa dmar nas kyang bka' drin che ba'i bla ma gcig pur mdzad /
NG0859:15365: gzhan yang bka' gter gyi bstan pa sgo du ma
NG0859:15366: nas spel bzhin par dgung lo dgu bcu tham pa
NG0859:15367: lcags glang lor skur gshegs so ///
NG0859:15368: / zhwa dmar bzhi pa spyan snga rin po che tre shod khang dmar du /
NG0859:15369: yab ldong dgon pa skyabs dang yum dbra bza' bsod nams sgrol ma'i sras su 'khrungs /
NG0859:15370: zur mang dgon rje bdun pa chos grags rgya mtsho dang mjal te rab du byung */
NG0859:15371: mtshan chos kyi grags pa ye shes dpal bzang por gsol /
NG0859:15372: mkhan po go shri grags dpal pa dang */
NG0859:15373: pan sgar pa las kyang chos gsan / @#//
NG0859:15374: dgung lo nyer bzhi pa la 'gos lo chen po
NG0859:15375: yid bzang rtse bas mkhan po mdzad de bsnyen par
NG0859:15378: gsang 'jigs sogs gsar ma'i rgyud sde rnams dang */
NG0859:15379: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po'i dbang bka' dang bshad
NG0859:15380: pa'i bka' thams cad sogs snga phyir gsan pa mtha'
NG0859:15381: yas pa mdzad / ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs
NG0859:15382: kyi gdungs rigs lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho las
NG0859:15383: kyang gsar rnying gi chos mang du gsan /
NG0859:15384: rje 'gos las phur pa'i dbang gsan tshe mnal lam
NG0859:15385: du slob dpon pad+ma zhal gzigs shing gdam pa'ang bstsal
NG0859:15386: / gsar rnying gi chos tshul mtha' dag gdul bya
NG0859:15387: rnams la ston bzhin pa'i ngang nas dgung lo don
NG0859:15388: gsum pa la gzugs sku brtul /
NG0859:15389: don dam nges 'byed dbu ma chen po'i lha khr-id rgyal tshab chen po'i chos nga la brten cing */
NG0859:15390: chos skad mthar thug pa phyir mi ldog pa'i gtam
NG0859:15391: gtso bor bzhed pa rje 'di kun mkhyen chen po
NG0859:15392: klong chen pa / karma pa bdun pa /
NG0859:15393: kun mkhyen dol bu chen po sogs mthun no ///
NG0859:15394: / de nyid kyis 'bri gung zur pa rin chen phun tshogs la bstsal ba ste /
NG0859:15395: 'di ni dbur stod 'bri gung sku gnyer sgang zhes bya bar skyu ra'i rigs su sku bltams /
NG0859:15396: dgung lo brgyad kyi steng du spyan snga rin po che chos kyi grags pa las rab tu byung */
NG0859:15397: bcu gsum par rtsis thang bsam gtan gling du dkar
NG0859:15398: po bas khrag 'brug gi zhig gsos mdzad pa'i rab
NG0859:15399: gnas la spyan drangs pa'i tshe ngo mtshar ba'i cho
NG0859:15403: gzho stod til gro sogs gnas chen rnams su sgrub pa la snying por mdzad /
NG0859:15404: ti grol bzhugs pa'i skabs shed 'phags yul gyi grub
NG0859:15405: thob rdo rje mgon po byon nas dza bi ra'i
NG0859:15406: b+hu rlung gi man ngag sogs gdams pa dang rjes
NG0859:15408: mkha' 'gro'i lung bstan bzhin sku rten dkar chag tu
NG0859:15409: bsgyur zhing yangs pa can du gter gyi kha byang
NG0859:15410: babs pa bzhin gu ru rin po che'i sku gsung
NG0859:15411: thugs bcud dam chos dgongs pa yang zab shog ser
NG0859:15412: rigs lnga til gro'i da ki'i tshogs khang chen mo
NG0859:15413: nas spyan drangs / dus gzhan zhig tu zangs mdog
NG0859:15414: dpal rir byon nas gu ru rin po che he
NG0859:15415: ru ka'i rnam par mjal zhing ga na tsakra'i 'du
NG0859:15417: rtsa ba gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas dbang
NG0859:15418: bskur zhing gdams pa dang rjes su gdams pa thams
NG0859:15419: cad bstsal te he ru ka'i sku slob dpon pad+mar
NG0859:15420: gnas 'gyur bas zhal gyi man ngag kyang mang du
NG0859:15421: gnang nas slar rang gnas su phebs /
NG0859:15422: bka' gter gnyis kyi bdag por gyur /
NG0859:15423: mdo sgyu sems gsum la bshad srol thun mong ma yin pa dang */
NG0859:15426: gter kha gong 'og sogs la rtsal du bton cing
NG0859:15427: 'chad nyan gyi phrin las shin tu rgya che zhing
NG0859:15429: po che'i phyag srol ltar bka' mas khog dbub /
NG0859:15430: gter ma'i man ngag gis brgyan pa zhigs phyag len du 'debs par mdzad do //
NG0859:15431: des rang grol nyi zla sangs rgyas la sgyu 'phrul skor rnams gsungs /
NG0859:15432: des 'khon rigs slob dpon tshe dbang nor rgyas la
NG0859:15433: bshad cing des khong nyid kyi sras 'khon ston dpal
NG0859:15435: rje 'di nyid yab slob dpon de dang */
NG0859:15436: yum rgyal mo 'dzom gyi sras su lcags bya lor 'khrungs /
NG0859:15437: chung ngu nas dam pa'i bag chags sad cing nges 'byung gi thugs yang dag pa skyes /
NG0859:15438: dgung lo bcu lon pa'i tshe thams cad mkhyen pa bsod nams rgya mtsho las rab tu byung */
NG0859:15440: thugs rje chen po'i sgom lung sogs gsan /
NG0859:15441: de sogs gsar rnying gi bla ma 'ga' las ci rigs pa'i chos tshul rnams thams cad gsan /
NG0859:15442: sgra'i ri mo dang snyan dngags /
NG0859:15444: gso rigs sogs la'ang bslabs sbyangs dpyis phyin par mdzad /
NG0859:15445: khyad par yab rdo rje 'dzin pa las sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po dang */
NG0859:15446: de'i 'grel pa g.yung ston gyis mdzad pa dang */
NG0859:15447: kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i phyogs bcu mun sel sogs
NG0859:15448: sgyu 'phrul skor gyi 'grel tika rnams la sbyangs par
NG0859:15449: mdzad pa na sgro phug pa chen po'i bag chags
NG0859:15450: sad pas lam 'di nyid la brten pa'i mkhas grub
NG0859:15452: dgung lo bco brgyad par gnubs nam mkha'i snying po'i
NG0859:15453: rnam 'phrul rig 'dzin chen po nyi zla sangs rgyas
NG0859:15454: kyi drung du rdzogs chen klong gsal snying thig gi
NG0859:15455: dbang khrid man ngag dang bcas pa gsan pas chos
NG0859:15456: thams cad kyi gnas lugs rdzogs pa chen po rang
NG0859:15457: rig chos kyi skur ngo 'phrod cing gting sleb /
NG0859:15458: gzhan yang bka' gter gyi chos shin tu mang ba gsan /
NG0859:15459: khyad par don tig 'gro ba kun grol dang */
NG0859:15460: theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod la bshad lung gsan /
NG0859:15461: mdo phyogs kyi gzhung lugs chen po kun la'ang gsan
NG0859:15462: bsam mthar phyin par mdzad cing chos gra chen po
NG0859:15463: rtses dang du gzhung lugs rab 'byams smra ba'i gra
NG0859:15464: skor mdzad / brag dgon spyan snga gzhon nu chos
NG0859:15465: dpal las rdo rje phreng ba sogs gsar rnying gi
NG0859:15467: dgung lo so bzhi par rgyal khang rtse ba dpal
NG0859:15468: 'byor rgya mtsho dang chos kyi rje dge 'dun rgyal
NG0859:15469: mtshan pa mkhan slob las bsnyen par rdzogs pa'ang mdzad
NG0859:15470: nas mtshan dpal 'byor lhun grub tu gsol /
NG0859:15471: dge lugs phyogs kyi sngags skor rnams kyang gsan /
NG0859:15472: gsang phu dang se ra byes kyi 'chad nyan slob dpon pa'ang mdzad /
NG0859:15473: rgyud gsang ba snying po la sngar bshad srol ches
NG0859:15474: dar yang phyis nyag phra bar gyur pas rje 'di
NG0859:15475: nyid mkhyen pa che ba'i grags pas /
NG0859:15476: brag sna chos rje u rgyan bstan 'dzin ched gnyer
NG0859:15477: gyis byon te g.yung 'grel kyi steng nas zhib par
NG0859:15478: gsan cing le'u lnga pa yan gyi zin bris kyang
NG0859:15480: par zur 'khor lo'i mgon po chos dbyings rang grol
NG0859:15481: rjes su bzung zhing gsang ba snying po g.yung 'grel
NG0859:15482: las nyin re chos thun gnyis re dang */
NG0859:15483: gzhan yang snying thig gi skor rnams sogs mtha' yas pa gsan /
NG0859:15484: rje'i bslab ston ltar zur chen gyis chos gra chen
NG0859:15485: po rtse dang du gra skor gyi bstan pa'i rnam
NG0859:15486: gzhag mdzad pas snga 'gyur la rgyud bshad med de
NG0859:15487: 'ong snyam pa'i phrag dog can rnams kha rog ste
NG0859:15489: spangs te / yul di wi ko ti'am pha wang kha'i nags khrod du dben pa brten cing bzhugs /
NG0859:15490: phyag na pad+ma lnga pa chen pos kyang zhabs la gtugs te /
NG0859:15491: gsar rnying gi dbang lung khrid man ngag gi skor mtha' yas pa gsan /
NG0859:15492: bla chen 'ga' zhig gis ltar grub mtha' gtsang gtsang
NG0859:15493: mo yin rgyu pa'i mtshan nyid pa skam po'i rigs
NG0859:15494: kyi shan ma shor ba dang dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NG0859:15495: mtshan nyid dang ldan pas zin pa'i rjes de 'dra'i
NG0859:15497: de nas dgung gi grangs don drug pa la rje
NG0859:15498: lnga pa chen pos zhabs brtan gyi gsol 'debs mdzad
NG0859:15499: pas da ste yun ring e sdod mi shes zhes
NG0859:15500: zhal gyis ma bzhes shing rnga yab pad+ma 'od kyi
NG0859:15501: gzhal yas su 'gro dgos pa zhes gsungs la /
NG0859:15502: me glang zla ba brgyad pa'i tshes bcu gcig la
NG0859:15503: ngo mtshar ba'i ltas dang bcas gzugs sku chos kyi
NG0859:15505: rje 'di nyid kyis mdzad pa'i bstan bcos kyang phyag
NG0859:15506: rdzogs dbu gsum gyi lta ba spyi khyab tu ngo
NG0859:15509: tha snyad rig pa'i skor yang mang po yod /
NG0859:15510: rje de'i thugs kyi sras slob ma ni zur chen
NG0859:15511: chos dbyings rang grol yin te 'di nyid zur gyi
NG0859:15512: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i gdungs rabs ma chad pa las
NG0859:15513: / yab rig 'dzin chen po ku ma ra dza'i
NG0859:15514: rnam 'phrul zur chen gzhon nu don 'grub dang yum
NG0859:15515: mkha' 'gro'i rigs las mtshan ldan yid 'dzin gnyis kyi
NG0859:15516: sras su shing 'brug lor sku bltams /
NG0859:15517: drung pa dkon mchog rin chen pa'i sku skye bar ngos 'dzin mdzad /
NG0859:15518: rim gyis yi ge 'bri klog dang 'phags yul gyi
NG0859:15519: yig rigs rnams kyang dka' tshegs la ma ltos par
NG0859:15520: thugs su chud / yab las nyer mkho'i sgrub skor rnams kyang bslab /
NG0859:15521: dgung lo dgu par byang ba rig 'dzin ngag gi
NG0859:15522: dbang po mjal zhing zhal nas sku skye bas snga
NG0859:15523: 'gyur gyi bstan pa la phan thogs chen po zhig
NG0859:15525: lha ris dang rtsis skor rnams dang drag sngags kyi
NG0859:15526: skor 'ga' zhig kyang mkhyen par mdzad cing dgung lo
NG0859:15527: bcu gnyis tsam nas snang gsal rin po che ngag
NG0859:15528: dbang ye shes grub pa'i zhabs su bcar te bka'
NG0859:15530: mkha' 'gro snying thig bka' gter gnyis /
NG0859:15531: bla ma nor bu rgya mtsho /
NG0859:15532: kar gling zhi khro dgongs pa rang grol sogs kyi dbang lung dang */
NG0859:15533: nyams khrid mthar phyin pa gsan /
NG0859:15535: yang ci rigs pa'i gter chos rnams gsan /
NG0859:15536: zhi khro'i dbang bskur ba'i gsang mtshan chos dbyings rang
NG0859:15537: grol du phog / phyag chen lnga ldan dang gcod
NG0859:15538: khrid sogs sku nyams su bstar /
NG0859:15539: zir pa stag mgor lo gsum phyogs gsum mdzad cing
NG0859:15540: gtso bor rdzogs chen mkha' 'gro snying thig gi ka
NG0859:15541: dag dang lhun grub gnad du bsnun pas chos thams
NG0859:15543: rang rig gdod ma'i mgon po'i rang zhal mngon du
NG0859:15544: gyur pa'i rtogs pa brnyes shing 'od gsal du longs
NG0859:15545: sku'i zhing khams nyul ba'i rtsal 'byongs par gyur /
NG0859:15546: dgung lo bcu bdun pa la rdo rje 'chang pha
NG0859:15547: wang kha pa dpal 'byor mtshan can gyi drung du
NG0859:15548: byon te bla ma sku 'das kyi bar la rim
NG0859:15549: gro ba mdzad cing mnyes pa gsum gyis bsten /
NG0859:15550: bla mas kyang thugs dgyes pas rjes su bskyangs nas
NG0859:15551: bka' gter kyi chos tshul rgya mtsho lta bu bum
NG0859:15552: pa gang byo'i tshul gyis gnang */
NG0859:15553: gtso bor dpal snying po'i rtsa rgyud rtsa ba dang */
NG0859:15555: bod 'grel g.yung tika rnams sbyar ba'i gsung bshad mdzad pa nyin re rtsi bzhag thun gnyis re bstsal /
NG0859:15556: zin dka' se pa la re zeg rgyab i chog zhus pas /
NG0859:15557: rgyang tsam ma song bar zin bris byas na 'jag
NG0859:15558: chen po ma yong bas re zhig nas nged kyis
NG0859:15559: tshod byed gsungs // gzim chung thog khar skyong sbyang
NG0859:15560: gnang nas shog bu sum cu tsam song nas rje'i
NG0859:15561: bka' bzhin zin bris kyang mdzad pas le'u lnga pa
NG0859:15562: tshod byed gsungs // yan chad song */ de man chad kyi zin bris 'phro can du lus /
NG0859:15563: chu khyi lor dgung lo nyi shu bzhes par slar
NG0859:15564: yang dge bsnyen nas bzung bsnyen rdzogs kyi bar du
NG0859:15565: bsgrubs par mdzad / snying 'grel phyogs bcu mun sel sogs la gzigs rtogs dang */
NG0859:15566: 'dus pa'i 'grel pa sgron gsal la bzhi sbrags kyi bshad pa /
NG0859:15568: bde mchog sbas don kun gsal /
NG0859:15569: nor bzang gi dus 'khor spyi don sogs dang */
NG0859:15570: gsang 'dus bskyed rdzogs sogs kyi bshad pa zhus shing thugs la nges par mdzad /
NG0859:15571: shing byi lor chos grwa chen po dpal gyi rtses
NG0859:15572: ngang du dgun chos chen mo'i thog gsang ba snying
NG0859:15573: po'i rgyud kyi bshad pa mdzad pas ston chen tshig
NG0859:15574: la rton pa rnams kyi spobs pa bcom zhing snying
NG0859:15575: po'i bstan pa la bya ba cher mdzad pas gzu
NG0859:15576: bor gnas pa rnams bsngags par brjod cing byang ba
NG0859:15577: rig 'dzin chen pos kyang legs dar dpyangs /
NG0859:15578: rje pha wang kha pa las kyang klong gsal snying
NG0859:15579: thig gi dbang lung man ngag gi khrid rnams zhib
NG0859:15580: par gsan zhing bsgoms pas nyams rtogs bogs sngar las
NG0859:15581: kyang cher 'khrungs / b+hai ra ba'i 'khrul 'khor sogs
NG0859:15582: gsar ma phyogs kyi drag sngags kyang mang du gsan
NG0859:15584: zhing 'bri gung zur pa rat+na'i zhabs sogs kyis ra
NG0859:15585: hu la'i las sbyor mdzad pas dga' ldan khri pa
NG0859:15586: mang po steng grib kyis gshegs pa la rje dkon
NG0859:15588: 'jug gi 'jigs pa las grol ba'i srung 'khor kyang mdzad /
NG0859:15589: kah thog pa stag bla pad+ma ma ti lha sar
NG0859:15590: byon nas snying po'i 'grel pa phyogs bcu mun ser
NG0859:15591: sogs gsan cing khong gis lho brag gsung sprul la'ang
NG0859:15592: de'i bshad lung phul ba sogs chos rgyun de ka
NG0859:15594: tshur kah thogs pa las dgongs 'dus po ti'i lung dbang dang rgyud dgu bcangs thabs bcas pa dang */
NG0859:15595: las byang me tog phreng mdzes sogs kyang gsan //
NG0859:15596: lhag par bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor
NG0859:15597: la brten pa'i sa ra ya na'i sgrub pa mdzad
NG0859:15598: / 'di skabs tsam nas rgyal mchog lnga pa chen
NG0859:15599: pos bla mar bkur zhing zil gnon sogs chos bka'
NG0859:15600: rnams gsan zhing drag sngags kyi skor sogs zhi rgyas
NG0859:15601: dbang drag gi phrin las rab 'byams kyi lung phyag
NG0859:15602: khrid thams cad phul zhing thugs nyams su bstar /
NG0859:15603: kar gtsang mchod yon gyis dge lugs spyi dang bye
NG0859:15604: brag dge ldan pho brang ba la sdang zug che
NG0859:15605: bas tsi kum par sde gzar gyi skabs su las
NG0859:15606: sbyor mtha' yas pa mdzad pas /
NG0859:15607: rgyal dbang lnga pa'i phrin las dus bab dang rje
NG0859:15608: 'di nyid kyi byin rlabs lhag par myur bas dge
NG0859:15609: ldan pho brang gi lung las bod khams yongs la
NG0859:15611: snum zan grong pa'i rkang 'thung 'khrig pa'i klung *//
NG0859:15612: khe nyin gsher gyis don chen 'grub pa'i zhugs //
NG0859:15613: 'bar min ma babs las kyi rta gdong mes //
NG0859:15614: sgar gtsang srid sde'i chu bo skem de mtshar //
NG0859:15615: zhes lnga pa chen pos dge phyogs rnams kyis mngon
NG0859:15616: spyod kyi nus pa mngon du ma gyur bar 'os
NG0859:15617: med kyi rje 'di pas bstan pa spyi la sman
NG0859:15618: yon chen por gyur pa'i ched du brjod par mdzad
NG0859:15619: do // gzhan yang phur pa lugs gsum dang bka' brgyad lugs gsum /
NG0859:15620: rdzogs pa chen po klong gsal snying thig sogs kyi
NG0859:15621: nyams khrid rnams gsan pa sku nyams su bstar bas
NG0859:15622: rdzogs pa chen po'i nyams myong ma 'khrul pa thugs
NG0859:15623: rgyud la 'khrungs shing 'khor 'das re dogs dang bral
NG0859:15626: gnas gsar ba mgon po bsod nams mchog ldan dang yang chos kyi dga' ston stob res mdzad /
NG0859:15627: byang ba rig 'dzin ngag gi dbang po'i sprul pa'i
NG0859:15628: sku snga 'gyur bstan pa'i nyi ma rig 'dzin pad+ma
NG0859:15629: phrin las ngos 'dzin par mdzad cing thub bstan rdo
NG0859:15630: rje brag gi gdan sar bkod nas /
NG0859:15631: bka' gter gyi chos mtha' dag bstsal zhing bstan pa'i bdag por mnga' gsol /
NG0859:15632: sku tshe'i mthar 'gro dgon skye med zhing gi gdan sa gung thang du bzhugs /
NG0859:15633: dar sding rig 'dzin chen po 'phrin las lhun grub la snying po'i rgyud kyi bshad pa gnang */
NG0859:15634: tshur yang bka' brgyad sogs dbang lung mang du gsan pa dang */
NG0859:15635: rgya bod hor gsum gyi bla ma skye sbrul sogs
NG0859:15636: chos don gnyer rnams la bka' gter gsar rnying gis
NG0859:15637: rnam par grol ba'i lam gyi dngos
NG0859:15639: [(]19[)]@#// po ci rigs par sbyor bar mdzad nas sa bya
NG0859:15640: lor rad gung grangs re drug lon pa na ngo
NG0859:15641: mtshar gyi ltas dang bcas pa pad+ma 'od kyi zhing
NG0859:15643: rje 'di nyid la thugs sras slob ma'i tshogs bgrang gis mi spyod par bzhugs kyang */
NG0859:15644: gtso bor gyur pa ni rgyal mchog lnga pa chen
NG0859:15645: po ste zhing khams gzhan du gshegs pa'i tshe yang
NG0859:15646: ye shes kyi skus rjes su bzung bar gsungs shing
NG0859:15647: rnam thar rgyal ba mchog gi zhal gsum mar /
NG0859:15648: legs byas 'di mthun rigs rtsal kun tu bzang *//
NG0859:15649: mngon sum rang ngo 'phrod min de srid du //
NG0859:15650: skye bar mgon po khyod kyis dge ba'i bshes //
NG0859:15651: mdzad nas 'bral pa med par rjes 'dzin shog //
NG0859:15652: / ces gsungs pas kyang mtshon par nus so //
NG0859:15653: 'dis gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes kyi rnam 'phrul
NG0859:15654: gnyos ston chen po phrin las lhun 'grub la gsang
NG0859:15655: ba snying po'i bshad rgyun spar khab dang g.yung tika
NG0859:15656: gnyis ka'i steng nas bstsal zhing */
NG0859:15657: de las bai ro dang g.yu sgra'i thugs bskyed dus
NG0859:15658: su smin pa rig 'dzin 'gyur med rdo rje sku
NG0859:15659: mched kyi bka' drin las deng sang gi bar du
NG0859:15660: rgyun ma chad par byung ba yin no ///
NG0859:15661: / yang sgro phug pa chen po'i slob brgyud 'phyong
NG0859:15662: rgyas rgya sman pa sangs rgyas grags zhes bya ba
NG0859:15663: ni / rus gnya' yul rgya sman stag rtse sar 'khrungs /
NG0859:15664: gzhon nu'i dus dzam+b+ha la bsgrubs pas zhing chung zhig yod pa de'ang chus khyer /
NG0859:15665: bya bral la byon pas spu gu dor phyug po
NG0859:15666: mdzes khyer ba zhig gi ro khur mi ma 'byung
NG0859:15667: bar 'dug / snying rje drag po skyes te rtog
NG0859:15668: med mdzad nas ro las byas pas mal 'gram nas
NG0859:15670: des dzam+b+ha las dngos grub byin par 'dug / slar
NG0859:15671: log te gra phyi khang dmar du khyung po khro
NG0859:15672: bo thug / khong yang dag bsgrub pa'i phyag phyir
NG0859:15674: yang dag mar me dgu pas zhal gzigs /
NG0859:15676: gsang bdag sgro phug pa'i slob ma bya chen po'i
NG0859:15677: dbon po zhig la mdo dang sgyu 'phrul la sogs
NG0859:15679: der phyug po zhig gi nas khal brgya tham pa phul /
NG0859:15680: cha rkyen gyis mi 'thogs par byung bas sgro phug pa'i slob ma nyang nag mdo bo /
NG0859:15681: de'i slob ma lha rjes mda' seng gi las sgyu 'phrul nyan /
NG0859:15682: mkhas pa chen por gyur nas /
NG0859:15683: rang yul du rdo thog thel btab /
NG0859:15684: gnyal pa zhig po'i slob ma rgya 'ching ru pas
NG0859:15685: kyang rdo thog pa'i zhabs la gtugs te thos pa
NG0859:15686: mang du mdzad / khyad par du 'di la slob
NG0859:15687: ma mkhas shing grub pa'i dpa' bo skyi chos kyi
NG0859:15688: seng ge bya ba zhig byung */
NG0859:15689: des gong ma se chen gyi spyan sngar byon pas /
NG0859:15690: rgyal pos nus pa brtag pa'i phyir thub chod mdzad
NG0859:15691: de mchod rten gyi nang du bcug nas sgo brtsigs
NG0859:15692: te lo gcig bzhag / lo dus na phye ste
NG0859:15693: bltas pas / rdo rje phur bu'i skur gyur 'dug pas ngo mtshar chen po skyes /
NG0859:15695: pa la dar ring chen mo la sogs pa'i dngos po tshan chen gnang */
NG0859:15696: 'ja' sas bcad pa'i dgon gzhis kyang mang du yod de dar rgyas shin tu che ba byung */
NG0859:15697: da lta ni ming du grags pa'i rjes shul tsam
NG0859:15698: ste bstan pa'i 'phel 'grib 'di yang skyo ba bskul
NG0859:15700: skyi chos kyi seng ge'i slob ma ni /
NG0859:15702: 'di ni 'phyong po'i kha ru'i nyang ston chen por
NG0859:15703: sras lnga byung ba yar klung sprul sku mched lngar
NG0859:15705: yul yar klung dgon pa sman lung yin pas de skad du grags /
NG0859:15706: tshigs gnyis pa chos ldan pa'i gdan sa da lta chos ldan zhes pa'i dgon rol 'di ka yin /
NG0859:15707: mtshan dngos mgon po rdo rje zhes bya ba ste
