NG0859:17637: 'gro mgon nyang ral ras chung rdor grags dang *//
NG0859:17638: rgyal sras dbang chen glo bo yab sras dang *//
NG0859:17639: chag lo chos dpal khro phu lo tswa dang *//
NG0859:17640: nag tsho lo tsa kun mkhyen mus srad pa /
NG0859:17641: mkhas grub bsod bzang grub chen dmar zhabs dang *//
NG0859:17642: dam pa sangs rgyas bai ro bi ma la //
NG0859:17643: u rgyan yab yum rgyal po khri srong dang *//
NG0859:17644: ma gcig lab sgron zhang la ras chen pa //
NG0859:17645: khams pa sga lo rgya gar pan chen rnams //
NG0859:17648: kun kyang nga ni pad+ma dbang rgyal yin //
NG0859:17649: smra zhing thams cad khyod la thim nas song *//
NG0859:17651: nyer gsum pa la glo bo lo tsa ba lam 'bras tshogs bshad dang */
NG0859:17653: nyer bzhi pa'i tshe yang tshar gcig bskyar /
NG0859:17655: bsam grul gling du glo bo mkhan chen bsod nams lhun grub gyis mkhan po /
NG0859:17656: chos rje dkon mchog skyabs kyis slob dpon /
NG0859:17657: de bzhin du gsang ston pa /
NG0859:17660: dad pa'i dge slong nyi shu rtsa lnga dang bcas pa'i dbus su /
NG0859:17661: bu lugs kyi las chog gzhir bzhag la /
NG0859:17663: 'phags pa rin po che'i las chog gi bshad sbyar
NG0859:17664: dang bcas tshig gsum gyis bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i dngos
NG0859:17665: por bsgrubs / mkhan slob de rnams las chos kyang mang du nyan /
NG0859:17666: nyer drug pa la shel gyi ri bo 'brug sgra la sogs pa'i dben par /
NG0859:17670: lhung bzed las gzhan pa'i yo byad thams cad spangs te sgo gcig pa'i brtul zhugs bzung */
NG0859:17671: ston pas bcas pa'i gnang bkag dang */
NG0859:17672: sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis la sgra ji bzhin
NG0859:17673: par gnas pa ni skyes bu chen po 'di dang
NG0859:17674: kong po rgod tshang pa sna tshogs rang grol gyi
NG0859:17675: rnam par thar pa mthong ba'i chos la gnas nges
NG0859:17676: par shes / gzhan du mi la ras pa la
NG0859:17677: sogs te rtags dang cho ga ma byas pa'ang ji
NG0859:17678: snyed cig yod srid kyi de dag la bstan pa
NG0859:17679: la dga' ba'i lha rnams dang lhan cig rjes su
NG0859:17681: slar ljongs rgyu ba'i brtul zhugs kyis mnga' ris kyi gnas rten rnams kyang mjal /
NG0859:17682: theg pa chen po'i bslab par bya ba'i gnas las
NG0859:17683: 'da' ba ma yin pas chos kyi sbyin pa'ang ci
NG0859:17684: rigs su bstsal / glo bo mkhan chen las /
NG0859:17688: gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa mang du gsan /
NG0859:17690: gu ge pan chen rnam rgyal dpal bzang */
NG0859:17691: 'jam dbyangs blo gros dpal mgon rnams la sgra dang */
NG0859:17694: gsang sngags kyi dbang dang man ngag kyang mang du nyan /
NG0859:17697: kho char la sogs pa'i gnas rten 'khor nas slar glo bor byon /
NG0859:17698: drang so gter ston shakya bzang po las byang gter mang du gsan /
NG0859:17699: mdor na bde kye gsang gsum /
NG0859:17713: phyag chen sbyor drug / u rgyan bsnyen bsgrub /
NG0859:17717: sogs te gsar rnying bka' gter bstan bcos /
NG0859:17718: man ngag gi yi ge rnam pa thams cad la
NG0859:17719: da ri dra'i brtul zhugs kho nas chos sgugs sogs
NG0859:17720: kyi ngal ba dang du blangs te /
NG0859:17722: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NG0859:17723: 'chi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos btsal //
NG0859:17724: zhes pa ni skyes bu dam pa 'dis phyag len la btab pa yin /
NG0859:17725: gsar rnying gi rgyud sde chen po de dag la 'ang bsnyen pa ma song ba med pas /
NG0859:17726: deng snga 'gyur ba tshos bka' brgyad dang */
NG0859:17727: gsar ma pa rdo rje phreng ba tsam gyis bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'ang dkon pa'i dngos por gyur na /
NG0859:17729: dam pa'i chos 'tshol zhing bya btang sgo gcig pa'i brtul zhugs kyis bal yul shing kun /
NG0859:17733: yang le shod la sogs pa thams cad du gshegs
NG0859:17734: shing de dag tu bal bod kyi bla ma mang
NG0859:17735: po bsnyen / gnas 'brel dang thugs dam 'ba' zhig mdzad /
NG0859:17736: dag pa'i snang ba mtha' klas par shar /
NG0859:17737: yi dam dang chos skyong mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NG0859:17738: mkha' 'gro mas slob dpon a b+h+ya ka ra'i skye bar lung bstan /
NG0859:17739: lo chen dkon mchog skyabs kyis rdo rje phreng ba'i dbang la dogs cha mdzad pas /
NG0859:17740: mtshan lam na 'khor lo sdom pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NG0859:17741: gtso bo pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal gyis mdzad cing
NG0859:17742: 'dug pa'i sgo drung nas mkha' 'gro mas khong bkag
NG0859:17743: nas ma btang bas slar 'gyod de gnang */
NG0859:17744: zhar la lam 'bras gsar ma'ang thob /
NG0859:17745: so brgyad pa nas gsar rnying ris med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo rgya chen po bskor /
NG0859:17746: de nas dbus gtsang gi phyogs la gsar rnying gi
NG0859:17747: chos rgyun nyams pa dag gso ba'i thugs bskyed bla
NG0859:17748: na med pas / yab dang glo bo'i sde ba dag kun la gnang ba zhus /
NG0859:17751: byang 'am ring rnams brgyud de byon /
NG0859:17752: bde grol du me ston nam mkha' rgyal mtshan dang */
NG0859:17753: sngags 'chang shakya bzang po gnyis mjal /
NG0859:17754: de nas gcung legs ldan kyang lhan cig pas dbus la byon /
NG0859:17755: chos tshigs sprul pa'i rdo rje gdan lha sa'i gtsug
NG0859:17756: lag khang jo shaka rnams kyis gtsos pa'i rten brten
NG0859:17757: pa rnams mjal / rngog chos dang zhi byed la
NG0859:17758: thugs 'dun drag po yod pas rje btsun ma dang
NG0859:17759: pa rnams mjal / */ dpal lha'i sprul pas bskor lam du 'grogs nas lung bstan /
NG0859:17760: gung thang du phyag mchod mdzad /
NG0859:17761: gzhung spre zhing du rngog bsod nams bstan 'dzin las rngog dkyil rnams legs par nod /
NG0859:17762: gro thang du zha lu lo chen chos skyong bzang po las gshed dmar skor sogs gsan /
NG0859:17763: bsam yas su byon pas sngon btsan po khri srong
NG0859:17764: lde'u btsan du gyur pa'i bag chags du ma sad
NG0859:17765: / bar khang du bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas sgrub mchod dang smon lam mdzad /
NG0859:17767: sogs la chos kyi bdud rtsi mang du bkye /
NG0859:17768: kah thog pa chos rje bsod nams rgyal mtshan sogs
NG0859:17769: bshes gnyen mang dag dang chos skyes 'bul res mdzad
NG0859:17770: / phreng po u rgyan chos rdzong du kong chen
NG0859:17771: nam mkha' dpal ldan las bla ma dgongs 'dus gsan
NG0859:17772: / / yang rdzong dang mchims phur thugs dam mdzad
NG0859:17773: pas rtsa ba gsum gyi lha tshogs mang po'i zhal
NG0859:17774: / / gzigs / chos dbang gi gdung rabs brgyad pas lho brag tu spyan drangs nas /
NG0859:17778: smra bo cog / gro bo lung la sogs par byon /
NG0859:17779: mnga' bdag nyang la u rgyan chen pos lung bstan pa bzhin /
NG0859:17780: pan chen 'dis chos brgyud nyams pa gso bar gsungs
NG0859:17781: pa'i bden pa'i rnga bo che sgrog pa'i dus la
NG0859:17782: babs te / nyang gi gdung sgar zur la rang lugs kyi bshad nyan rgya chen po mdzad /
NG0859:17783: sdig can 'ga' zhig la gnas spor mdzad pas 'ja' 'od kyis bar snang bkang */
NG0859:17784: zha stod dang btsan gro sogs su bsgrub chen bde
NG0859:17785: gshegs 'dus pa'i sman bsgrub dang skye bdun gyis 'gro
NG0859:17786: don mdzad / spyir skyes bu chen po 'di chos
NG0859:17787: la gnas 'jog shin tu che zhing khyad par sngon
NG0859:17788: gyi smon lam las bde gshegs 'dus pa la don
NG0859:17789: gnyer chen po dang ldan pas rang gi yab rje
NG0859:17790: la sogs par bka' brgyad bde 'dus tshar nyi shu
NG0859:17791: rtsa lnga gsan pa'i phyi ma khungs btsun zhing yid
NG0859:17792: rton par nus pa de lho brag dgon dkar zhes
NG0859:17793: pa 'dir ri brag la thogs pa med pa'i rje
NG0859:17794: rigs nam mkha'i rnal 'byor las rnyed pas gsan yig
NG0859:17795: tu'ang bsngags pa chen po mdzad cing */
NG0859:17796: dgongs pa mthar thug pa rdzogs pa'i tha tshig kyang gsal /
NG0859:17797: slar zhe drug par bsam yas su byon nas bka'
NG0859:17798: 'dus phyi ma rig 'dzin yongs 'dus kyi chos skor
NG0859:17799: rnams rnam snang gsang sgrom nas spyan drangs /
NG0859:17800: snye mor dgongs 'dus kyi sgrub chen btsugs /
NG0859:17801: phung po ri bo cher bde 'dus la 'chad nyan mdzad /
NG0859:17802: ngor dang gser mdog can du dge tshul slong gi las chog mang du mdzad /
NG0859:17803: gzhan yang chos 'chad nyan la sogs pa'i 'gro phan
NG0859:17804: rgya chen po mdzad de chu bo ri brgyud brag
NG0859:17805: rdo rje zhes pa 'dir zhag gcig gdan chags pas
NG0859:17807: brag chen phur pa zhes pa'i dpyad las bskyed rdzogs
NG0859:17808: kyi bstan pa zin pa'i brda' don dgongs pa bzhin
NG0859:17809: / slar phreng po pa dar zhing rgyas pa'i tshe
NG0859:17810: kun gzigs phreng po gter chen shes rab 'od zer
NG0859:17811: ti shrir bkur nas gnas 'dir yun ring por dgon
NG0859:17813: gsung rab mang po'i sbyar bya du'ang thub bstan rdo
NG0859:17814: rje brag tu sbyar ba'o zhes ming gi mnga' gsol
NG0859:17815: / de nas pan chen rin po che nyid phal cher bsam yas bu tshal du gtan chags /
NG0859:17816: byams pa gling du thu btsun bsod nams rnam rgyal las sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gsan cing */
NG0859:17818: zab chos mkha' 'gro snying tig gi dbang khrid ma lus pa phul nas thugs yid gcig tu 'dres /
NG0859:17819: 'o na smon thang du'ang sku mched lhan cig pas yun ring par bzhugs /
NG0859:17820: gcung rig 'dzin legs ldan pa bde lugs gnyis ka'i
NG0859:17821: pho sgo yangs pas 'bri gung pa rin chen phun
NG0859:17822: tshogs bsam yas su gdan drangs nas dpon slob gsum
NG0859:17823: ka bsam yas kyi rab gnas bskyar te bod khams
NG0859:17824: yun du bde ba'i rten 'brel bsgrigs /
NG0859:17825: 'di nas bzung chos rgyal rin chen phun tshogs kyang
NG0859:17826: sras kyi dam par gyur pas rgyal dbang pad+ma'i ring
NG0859:17827: lugs la rten 'brel chen por gyur /
NG0859:17828: spyir skyes bu 'di nyid ni gnas lnga rigs pa'i pan+di ta chen po /
NG0859:17829: mdo sngags gsar rnying ris med pa'i bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi dge ba'i gshes gnyen chen po /
NG0859:17830: bzhon pa dang 'jol bel la sogs pa'i chos brgyad
NG0859:17831: yongs su spangs pas shakya thub pa'i rjes zhugs bsod
NG0859:17833: zhen log dang dka' spyad khur du bzod pas bya btang rnal 'byor gyi dbang po chen po /
NG0859:17834: rig pa dang grol ba'i spobs pa bsam gyis mi
NG0859:17835: khyab pas byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun chen po
NG0859:17836: des dngos kyi lam nas bstan pa dang sems can
NG0859:17837: gyi don bla na med pa mdzad /
NG0859:17838: snga 'gyur rgyud 'bum rin po'i skor tsho 'byed pa'ang rnam dpyod 'di kho na che zhing */
NG0859:17839: lung gi rgyun la'ang bka' drin bsam gyis mi khyab /
NG0859:17840: tshig nyung la don shin tu mang ba sdom pa
NG0859:17841: gsum gyi rnam par nges pa'i bstan bcos la sogs
NG0859:17842: te / rnam grangs mtha' yas dag gis brgyud nas
NG0859:17843: bstan 'gro'i don bla na mtho ba'i cho ga mdzad
NG0859:17844: de 'on smon thang nas zangs mdog dpal gyi ri
NG0859:17845: te / bor gshegs so /// / da ni slob
NG0859:17846: dpon bai ro tsa na slar yang rigs grol gyis
NG0859:17847: sprul pa'i sgyu 'phrul la chags pa kun mkhyen shes
NG0859:17848: rab 'od zer gyi gtam bshad par bya ste /
NG0859:17849: bdag nyid chen po 'di ni byang ngam chen gyi
NG0859:17850: sa'i char khri bsam gnyis kyi cho 'brang las sa
NG0859:17851: pho stag lo chu stod zla ba'i tshe bcur mngal
NG0859:17853: lhums su zhugs pa'i tshe skyes bu shel gyi kha
NG0859:17854: dog can rin po che'i do shal dang ldan pa
NG0859:17855: zhig gis shel bum bdud rtsis gang ba yum gyi
NG0859:17856: spyi bo nas bstims pa rmis /
NG0859:17857: tshe bcu byung res sbra khyim la 'ja' zug pa dang */
NG0859:17858: dri zhim po'i ngad pa rgyun du byung */
NG0859:17859: gzhon nu rol rtsed kyi tshe na'ang */
NG0859:17861: dad pa'i snang ba rgya chen po /
NG0859:17862: myur la zab pa'i shes rab la sogs te byang
NG0859:17863: chub sems dpa'i ngang tshul gyis lhag par phyug pa
NG0859:17866: gnyan mgon rnams kyis zhal bstan pa byung ba 'bri
NG0859:17867: gung pas g.yag sde pan chen gyi bag chags su
NG0859:17868: ngos 'dzin mdzad / khyad par du rin chen phun
NG0859:17869: tshogs chos kyi rgyal po ji lta ba zhig gi
NG0859:17870: ngos 'dzin mdzad / zhal nas / khyod kyi snying ga @#//
NG0859:17871: na a zhig yod pa da lta ston mar na
NG0859:17872: zhes phyag mdzub btsugs pas brjod mi shes pa'i nyams
NG0859:17873: shar / rjes su sku'i bkod pa de kho nar snang zhes gsung */
NG0859:17874: ru skor de la hor gyis brgyab dus bu chung
NG0859:17875: 'phrog par brtsams te zhags pas btab pa na lhag
NG0859:17876: pa'i lhas sgrib par gzigs te bros pas thar /
NG0859:17877: de nas grog gi phur bzhugs /
NG0859:17878: byis pa'i dbus na chos gsung pa dang */
NG0859:17879: mdo rgyud kyi tshig tshon po cal col du 'don pa dang */
NG0859:17880: lhag par gzhon nu shes ma bye ba des chu
NG0859:17881: ban gang rgya can kha khyer nas bzung ste ja
NG0859:17883: rgan pa dag gis sgo bcad nas phyir thon pa na /
NG0859:17884: sgo ma phye bar thal byung du phyir thon pa sogs byung */
NG0859:17885: khyad par theg pa chen po'i rigs sad pas sems
NG0859:17886: can nyam chung ba dag la bzod du med pa'i
NG0859:17887: snying rje dang */ zhang pos 'thos pa'i gal la
NG0859:17888: ci mi snyam pas ka ca ster ba sogs phal
NG0859:17889: ba'i kun tu spyod pa las rgyang ring */
NG0859:17890: dgung lo brgyad pa'i tshe e wam gling smad dang
NG0859:17891: nyin sdings gnyis ka'i slob dpon brtan mkhas kyi yon
NG0859:17892: tan rdzogs pa tshul khrims 'od zer ba las dge
NG0859:17893: bsnyen du mdzad / mchod gral gyi lha phal cher
NG0859:17894: ngos 'dzin mdzad pas 'di shes rab thod rgal ba
NG0859:17895: zhig byung zhes mtshan shes rab 'od zer du btags
NG0859:17896: bsnyen du mdzad / / gser mdog can pa'i slob
NG0859:17897: ma'i mchog pan chen rdor rgyal ba las rab tu
NG0859:17898: bsnyen du mdzad / / byung */ de nas klog pa thos bsam gyi grar zhugs nas /
NG0859:17899: dga' ldan khri pa zhal snga nas bstan dar la zab mo lta ba dang */
NG0859:17900: rgya chen spyod pa'i sems bskyed lugs srol gnyis bslab btus /
NG0859:17901: spyod 'jug / mdo sde kun las btus /
NG0859:17904: klu sgrub lugs kyi don dam sems bskyed sogs nyan zhing klu sgrub gyi gzhung la nan tan ngos /
NG0859:17905: mtshan nyid kyi gzhung la lo drug gi bar du nyin mtshan med par sbyangs /
NG0859:17908: sa sde lnga sdom rnam gnyis /
NG0859:17914: dge ldan pa'i mdo'i lam rim gnyis /
NG0859:17915: sngags rim chen po la sogs te rgya bod kyi gzhung 'grel mang du nyan /
NG0859:17916: lam gyi 'gros la go don phun sum tshogs pa
NG0859:17917: skyes kyang 'khor ba'i sa bon drungs nas 'byin pa
NG0859:17918: lta ba rnam pa dag pa kho na yin /
NG0859:17919: de la dgag bzhag gi 'dod pa mang pos ngo bo ma 'khrul ba gang yin shes dka' /
NG0859:17920: sangs rgyas kyi lta ba zab mo ston pa la klu sgrub lung bstan /
NG0859:17921: de'i dgongs 'grel tshad ma zla ba grags pa yin /
NG0859:17922: des kyang sangs rgyas bskyangs la brten nas rtogs pa
NG0859:17923: yin pas 'grel pa bud+d+ha pa li ta la bslab
NG0859:17924: gnyer gting thug pa zhig byas pas /
NG0859:17925: deng sang lta ba'i gnas tshul gleng pa rnams la kho bo mgu po rang mi 'ong zhes gsungs /
NG0859:17926: sa dge gnyis car la mkhas pa'i slob @#//
NG0859:17927: dpon gcig yod pa las lugs gnyis ka'i sbyangs pa mthar son /
NG0859:17928: khyad par gsang ba 'dus pa la tsong kha pa
NG0859:17929: chen po'i yig che'i steng nas dgongs pa ji bzhin
NG0859:17930: du longs / rdor rgyal ba la dgyes rdor lha dgu /
NG0859:17932: rnam 'grel bcu gcig dang bcas pa /
NG0859:17933: gur brtag sam gsum lung ti ka bshad pa dang bcas pa /
NG0859:17935: lam rim pa gnyis kyi khrid /
NG0859:17936: bla ma dam pa'i ti ka'i steng nas gzabs bshad rnams dogs pa'i mtha' dpyad nas nyan pas /
NG0859:17938: dge bshes shes rab 'od zer 'dis chos kyi gnad
NG0859:17939: la bkar nas dri shes par 'dug ces 'chad pa
NG0859:17940: la bsnyengs pa bral ba dag blo gros la grim
NG0859:17942: rin po che rdor rgyal ba de las spyir mdo
NG0859:17943: sngags kyi gzhung 'grel da lta 'chad nyan yod pa
NG0859:17944: mtha' dag / de bzhin du gser mdog can pa
NG0859:17945: dang */ sa skya bka' 'bum yongs rdzogs mnyan nas /
NG0859:17947: lhag par gser mdog can pa'i yig cha la mchog tu 'dris shing grub mtha'ang 'dzin /
NG0859:17948: skyes bu dam pa 'di g.yag sde pan chen gyi
NG0859:17949: de ma thag pa'i skye ba yin pas sku gzhon
NG0859:17950: nu nas gsal snang shin tu che zhing khyad par
NG0859:17951: pan chen de la slob dpon chen pos seng gdong
NG0859:17952: ma'i gdams pa pu tir longs pa zhig bstsal ba
NG0859:17954: gzhan blor ma 'chud dogs nas mya ngan las 'da'
NG0859:17955: khar e wam rdo spyil du rgyas btab pa dus
NG0859:17957: 'brug pa rin po che pad+ma dkar po'ang gsal snang zhig la the tshom skyes pas /
NG0859:17959: de ni a khu mtshan nyid pa'i khrod du phyin
NG0859:17960: pas lan par 'dug ces gsungs pa bzhin rten 'brel
NG0859:17962: grwa sa de dang thal 'gyur gyi mgrin rnga ldir
NG0859:17963: ba'i rigs gra gang dang gang du rtsod pa'i g.yul
NG0859:17964: ngo la lhags pas blo gros bsam gyis mi khyab
NG0859:17965: pa song ste / bod 'grel rnams kyang rgya yan
NG0859:17966: du bzhag / rgyan drug mchog gnyis kyi gzhung 'grel
NG0859:17970: rigs pa gsum gyi lha'i rnga chen po kun nas kun tu yongs su brdungs pas /
NG0859:17971: gling sman slob dpon na re /
NG0859:17972: khyed slob gsar ba lta bu yin kyang 'di lta bu'i rnam dpyod kham che /
NG0859:17973: kun mkhyen rong po la bo dong pa'i dge bshes gcig gis /
NG0859:17975: kho bos phar phyin shes gsungs /
NG0859:17976: 'o na 'dul ba e gnang zhus pas /
NG0859:17977: de los shes phar phyin gyi spyod pa yin gsungs /
NG0859:17978: yang dbu tshad la dris pas /
NG0859:17979: de bzhin du dbu ma la lta ba dang */
NG0859:17980: tshad ma la rig lam yin gsungs pa ltar /
NG0859:17981: khyed kyis dbu phar la brten nas bstan pa'i sgrom 'tshol lugs /
NG0859:17982: de las rig lam gyi grub mtha' 'cha' lugs la dpags na /
NG0859:17983: dge bshes zer na 'di la zer zhes tshogs pa'i khrod rang @#//
NG0859:17984: du bsngags pa brjod pas de phyin nas dge bshes shes rab 'od zer zhes grags /
NG0859:17985: rtog ge'i rig pa la tsher ma lta bu'i blo gros mnga' yang */
NG0859:17986: 'di ltar skyes bu mchog tu gyur pa rnams ni de tsam la brten nas grags pa dang */
NG0859:17987: rnyed pa bsgrub pa'i sta gon rtsom pa ma yin pas /

NG0859:18928: mgon po bsod nams mchog ldan sogs gsar ma ste /
NG0859:18929: gsar rnying gi bla ma dam pa sum cu lhag
NG0859:18930: tsam bsten nas mdo sngags kyi chos mtha' yas pa
NG0859:18931: ngom pa med par gsan cing */
NG0859:18932: bye brag 'dus pa mdo'i dbang ni /
NG0859:18933: dgung lo brgyad pa la sngags 'chang kun bzang dpal
NG0859:18934: 'byor byang chub gling du spyan drangs te yab rje
NG0859:18935: dang lhan du zur lugs dang khams lugs gnyis gsan
NG0859:18936: / nyer gcig pa la lha btsun kun bzang rnam
NG0859:18937: rgyal la khams lugs kyi yi ge'i steng nas gsan
NG0859:18938: / / nyi shu rtsa dgu pa sa yos hor
NG0859:18939: zla bzhi pa la gong ra lhun grub sdings su+u
NG0859:18940: ma ha lo tsa ba gzhan phan rdo rje'i drung
NG0859:18941: du 'dus pa mdo'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NG0859:18942: dkyil 'khor thams cad rdul tshon gyis bzhengs par /
NG0859:18943: gnyal pa bde legs pa'i yi ge'i steng nas chu bo bzhi'i @#//
NG0859:18944: dbang gtad rgya sgom rim man ngag dang bcas pa
NG0859:18945: sgrub chen gyi las rim dang 'brel par zhag bcu
NG0859:18946: bdun gyi khongs su rdzogs par gsan /
NG0859:18947: gong lo de nyid skal ldan la chos sbyin lhag par bstsal ba las /
NG0859:18948: 'am bu chos mi 'tshong gsungs nas su'i yang chos yon mi bzhes par phyir slog par mdzad na'ang */
NG0859:18949: rje 'di'i dbang bum grwa tshang dgu phul ba mnyes mnyes kyis bdag gir mdzad ces grags te /
NG0859:18950: dbang gi chu bo'i snod du gzigs shing bstan pa
NG0859:18951: spel ba'i rten 'brel sgrig byed kyi brda' thabs bstan
NG0859:18952: par mngon / de ltar thos bsam gyi sgro 'dogs yin lugs su bcad nas /
NG0859:18953: dben pa'i gnas du mar snying po'i lam srol ji bzhin pa thugs nyams su bzhes pas /
NG0859:18954: ma dag pa'i snang ba 'gog nus pa'i bskyed rim
NG0859:18955: gyi gsal snang la reg mthong gi mtshan ma thob
NG0859:18956: ste / phrin las gang brtsams thogs med du 'grub /
NG0859:18957: rdzogs rim ka dag gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur med pa'i gnas lugs ji lta ba nyid rtogs pas /
NG0859:18959: snang srid lhun grub 'od gsal gyi klong du dwangs
NG0859:18960: pas yi dam gyi lha du ma'i gzigs snang shar
NG0859:18962: rang don yid byed kyi 'dzin pa zhig pas gzhan
NG0859:18963: phan mkha' khyab kyi thugs rje rtsol med shugs 'byung
NG0859:18964: gi sgo nas / thar pa dor gnyer gyi skal
NG0859:18965: ldan mchog dman mang po bshad sgrub kyi chos 'khor
NG0859:18966: rgyun chags su bskor bas bstan 'gro'i phan bde rgyas
NG0859:18967: gi sgo nas / par mdzad cing */ khyad par
NG0859:18968: sku gsung thugs kyi sras mchog gter chen chos kyi
NG0859:18969: rje la zab rgyas kyi chos thams cad tshang sprugs
NG0859:18970: su bstsal te rgyal tshab tu mnga' bskur nas /
NG0859:18971: dgung lo nga gnyis pa chu stag dbo zla'i nyer
NG0859:18972: gnyis la dbu gtsug phyur bur 'phar ba las zla
NG0859:18973: ba'i zil pa skya chil li ba dang spos dud
NG0859:18974: lta bu'i rlangs pa 'phro bzhin du gzugs sku'i bkod
NG0859:18975: pa chos kyi dbyings su bsdus so //
NG0859:18976: des lo chen chos rgyal bstan 'dzin rjes su bzung ste /
NG0859:18977: 'di ni e 'dam sngon po grong smad du lcags lug la 'khrungs /
NG0859:18978: sku tshe snga ma'i bag chags gsal bas grwa rigs
NG0859:18979: rnams kyis bdag sprad de dwags stod gling sogs gong
NG0859:18980: ma'i dgon pa rnams su spyan drangs /
NG0859:18981: bri klog dang chog phrin rnams tshegs med par thugs su chud nas /
NG0859:18982: 'phyong rgyas dpal ri grwa tshang du thugs gnyer la 'byon /
NG0859:18983: gdan sa ba bsod nams rin chen las rab tu byung zhing */
NG0859:18984: mtshan chos rgyal bstan 'dzin du gsol /
NG0859:18985: dbang lung yang ci rigs pa gsan /
NG0859:18986: dgongs 'dus la sogs pa'i cho ga'i tshig 'dzin dang */
NG0859:18987: de dag bri thig bcas dbyangs sogs nas brtsams te /
NG0859:18988: kun mkhyen chen po'i bstan bcos sems nyid ngal gso rtsa 'grel rnams la sbyangs /
NG0859:18989: der gnubs ston grags pa dbang po la yang bzlog dang lok+t+ri sogs drag @#//
NG0859:18990: sngags kyi lag len dang rtsis dkar nag kyang bslabs /
NG0859:18991: dgung lo bco brgyad pa sa pho byi ba'i lor
NG0859:18992: grwa sa'i dge bskos mdzad pas non che ba'i dper
NG0859:18994: lo de'i nang du rig 'dzin phrin las lhun grub 'phyong rgyas dpal rir spyan drangs te /
NG0859:18995: sprul pa'i sku mchog phrin las rnam rgyal gyis dbus
NG0859:18996: grwa gtsang yongs rdzogs la 'dus pa mdo'i dbang bskur
NG0859:18997: gdams ngag gtad rgya dang bcas pa rdul tshon gyi
NG0859:18998: dkyil 'khor du sgrub chen dang 'brel par zur lugs
NG0859:18999: dang */ zhar byung dpon slob nyung 'dus la ras
NG0859:19000: bris kyi steng nas khams lugs gnyis stsal ba'i tshe
NG0859:19002: phyis su'ang gnas dus ci rigs par bka' brgyad bde 'dus /
NG0859:19004: bi ma snying thig / zhig gling gi gter chos sogs mang du gsan /
NG0859:19005: gzhan yang lha btsun nam mkha' 'jigs med /
NG0859:19006: gsung sprul tshul khrims rdo rje sogs mkhas grub kyi
NG0859:19007: bla ma dam pa mang po bsten nas bka' gter
NG0859:19008: gyi dbang lung khrid bka' du ma dang */
NG0859:19009: rgya ri dpon pa'i lung gis bskul bas gong rar thegs te /
NG0859:19010: nyang ston blo mchog rdo rje la /
NG0859:19012: snyan ngag / sdeb sbyor sogs brda sprod yan lag dang bcas pa gsan te mkhyen par mdzad /
NG0859:19013: de ltar gsan pa rdzogs rjes e mthong smon dang mtsho mer steng du'ang ci rigs bzhugs shing */
NG0859:19014: gtso bor dwags stod gling gi dgon par stan 'jags
NG0859:19015: te sbas tshul gyis bsnyen sgrub la brtson par mdzad
NG0859:19017: srung ma las la khol ba'i mthu rtags nar mar
NG0859:19018: 'ong bas yul de dag gi grong pa rnams kyang
NG0859:19019: bla ma gling pa'i bka' dang 'gal na chos skyong
NG0859:19020: gi bka' chad 'ong zhes 'jigs par byed /
NG0859:19021: khyad par dgung lo so gnyis pa chu stag lor
NG0859:19022: dar gling du phebs te rje 'gyur med rdo rje
NG0859:19023: las pad gling gi chos bka' 'ga' zhig gsan /
NG0859:19024: de dus yab rje nas gsan pa'i mdo'i dbang rgyun
NG0859:19025: phyag bzhes dang bcas pa rnam par dag pa 'dug
NG0859:19026: par mkhyen te / phyis gdan sar spyan 'dren gnang
NG0859:19027: ba ltar byon nas rje gter chen bla ma la
NG0859:19029: snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa la phan pa bla na med par gyur /
NG0859:19030: dgung lo don brgyad pa sa byi hor zla bzhi
NG0859:19031: pa la dwags stod gling gi dgon par sku gshegs
NG0859:19032: so // de'ang bka' ma'i phyogs su zur mes dbon
NG0859:19033: gsum las slob ma'i rnam grangs ji ltar mched pa
NG0859:19035: de dag las mched pa'ang grangs med pas gang gi
NG0859:19036: ring la dar rgyas su mdzad pa gsang bdag sgro
NG0859:19037: phug pa chen po de gangs ri'i khrod na gsang
NG0859:19038: ba'i bdag po sngags kyi bstan pa spel ba'i slad
NG0859:19039: du byon to zhes pa de'ang grags pa don dang
NG0859:19040: ldan no // dus phyis ni gdul bya rdzogs pa
NG0859:19041: ltar gyur nas snyigs ma'i rgud pa stobs su gyur
NG0859:19042: ldan no // pas @#// snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa
NG0859:19043: bags kyis nyag phra ba'i ston gyi chu bran bzhin
NG0859:19044: bltar mi mngon pa'i gnas skabs su gangs can pa
NG0859:19045: rnams kyi gtsug rgyan slob dpon chen po bai ro
NG0859:19046: tsa na dang g.yu sgra snying po'i thugs bskyed phrag
NG0859:19047: par khyer bas phyogs mtha' dag nas gdams pa'i chu
NG0859:19048: rgyun phra mo thams cad bsdus te bstan pa'i chu
NG0859:19049: gter chen po mi 'dzad par bskyil bas mdo sgyu
NG0859:19050: sems gsum gyi ring lugs mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan
NG0859:19051: chen po gsar du slong bar byed pa ni gter
NG0859:19052: chen chos kyi rgyal po 'gyur med rdo rje dang
NG0859:19053: lo chen thams cad mkhyen pa ngag dbang chos dpal
NG0859:19054: yab sras slob ma'i tshogs dang bcas pa ste /
NG0859:19055: de la rje btsun gter chen dam pa 'di ni /
NG0859:19056: rang gter gab rgya can gyi lung bstan lasah bai
NG0859:19057: ro khyod ni skye mtha'i byang sems teh khyod kyi
NG0859:19058: 'di gong skye ba 'das pa nih smra bsam brjod
NG0859:19059: 'das ye shes snying po'i donah sems can sangs rgyas
NG0859:19060: mnyam nyid khyab gdal yang \u0f7f khams gsum 'gro ba'i
NG0859:19061: 'dren par rdo rje chosah shaka thub nye gnas a
NG0859:19062: nan+da zhes dang \u0f7f rgyal po dza dang shan+tim gar+b+ha
NG0859:19063: dang \u0f7f bod 'dir sam+b+ho ta sogs dag pa yih
NG0859:19064: skye ba de tsam snang gi ma dag pa'ih skye
NG0859:19065: tshul brjod du long ba'i gnas ma yinah de ltar
NG0859:19066: dag pa'i skye ba de dag gisah 'gro la snying
NG0859:19067: rje chen po'i thugs bskyed pa'ang \u0f7f bai ro khyod
NG0859:19068: du skye ba blangs pa yinah khyod kyang shri sid+ha
NG0859:19069: ye shes mdoh pad+ma bdag sogs gtsug gi bla mar
NG0859:19070: brtenah gdams pa'i gnad rnams phu thag bcad byas nasah
NG0859:19071: chos sku'i rang zhal mngon sum rtogs gyur pasah las
NG0859:19072: 'phro ma dag skye ba len mi sridah 'on kyang
NG0859:19073: sems bskyed smon lam bzang po yisah mtshams sbyor mtha'
NG0859:19074: yas 'gro ba'i dpal nyid duh dbang phyug 'bar dang
NG0859:19075: ra shag rdo rje gling \u0f7f kun skyong gling dang
NG0859:19076: mdo sngags gling pa sogasah pad+ma bdag gi zab gter
NG0859:19077: bdag po dang \u0f7f gzhan yang theg pa che chung
NG0859:19078: sna tshogs lah de dang mthun pa'i ngo mtshar skye
NG0859:19079: ba'i grangasah bcu phrag gcig dang gsum tsam 'das pa'i
NG0859:19081: gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje chos nyid gsang sngags kyi bstan pa spel ba'i phyir /
NG0859:19082: skal ldan rgyal po dza dang */
NG0859:19083: lo tsa ba chen po bai ro tsa na dang */
NG0859:19084: zur po che shakya 'byung gnas la sogs pa gang
NG0859:19085: la gang 'dul gyi sku'i bkod pa mtha' yas par
NG0859:19086: bstan nas don mdzad pa ste /
NG0859:19087: de yang snyigs ma lnga bdo'i dus 'dir bstan 'gro'i dpung gnyen du skye srid bzung ba'i tshul ni /
NG0859:19088: sku tshe snga ma'i sku rten 'chi srid 'od gsal gyi dbyings su bsdus pa las /
NG0859:19089: rig gdangs mkha' 'gro'i glus gzhan don du bskul ba'i rkyen gyis /
NG0859:19090: ye shes kyi sku he ru ka'i rnam par bzhengs nas lhums su zhugs te /
NG0859:19091: yab gnyos ston gsang bdag chen po phrin las lhun grub dang */
NG0859:19093: 'dzin dbyangs can sgrol ma'i sras su me khyi'i lo
NG0859:19094: dbo zla'i tshe bcu las g.yo zhing 'ja' 'od 'khrigs
NG0859:19095: pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas dang bcas te /
NG0859:19096: grwa nang dar rgyas chos gling du sku bltams /
NG0859:19097: btsas ma thag yab rjes blo rno ba'i rten 'brel dang */
NG0859:19098: bar chad bsrung ba'i dbang bskur byin brlabs du ma mdzad /
NG0859:19099: de dus kyi yul dang bya spyod kyi rnam pa dang */
NG0859:19100: de nas bzung ste lo gsum gyi bar dzo ki sngo sangs thor tshugs can zhig dang */
NG0859:19101: bud med mdzes ma gnyis kyi rgyun du sri zhu
NG0859:19102: byas pa'i dngos gnas rnams phyis kyang thugs la gsal
NG0859:19103: ba'i dran shes khyad par can mnga' /
NG0859:19104: pang du 'tsho ba'i dus nyid nas ting nge 'dzin
NG0859:19105: la dbang 'byor ba'i rnam 'gyur dang gzhon nu rol
NG0859:19106: rtsed kyi tshe yang rgyal ba'i rigs sad pa'i ngang
NG0859:19107: tshul dge bas blo ldan rnams dang bar mdzad /
NG0859:19108: dgung lo bzhi'i thog yab rje la bka' brgyad gsang
NG0859:19109: rdzogs kyi dbang gsan pa'i tshe yul snang thams cad
NG0859:19110: la dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor los rgyas thebs pa'i gtso
NG0859:19111: bo dang bla ma dbyer med du gzigs shing dbang
NG0859:19112: bzhi'i sa bon thugs rgyud la thebs pa nyid /
NG0859:19113: bcu pa shing lug gi ston bde 'dus kyi dbang
NG0859:19114: gsan dus 'od gsal gyi snang bar slob dpon chen
NG0859:19115: pos pad+mas dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus
NG0859:19116: pas 'phel te bum dbang gi nyams myong yul snang
NG0859:19117: sgyu ma lta bur gtan la phebs /
NG0859:19118: de yan chad du bri klog dang */
NG0859:19119: rang lugs kyi sgrub dkyil dbang rjes gnang rab gnas
NG0859:19120: lung sogs cho ga phrin rnams kyi tshig 'dzin dang
NG0859:19121: */ phyag bzhes thams cad tshegs med du chub ste /
NG0859:19122: de nas brtsams te yab rje'i sku tshab mdzad nas phrin las kyang ci rigs pa skyong bar mdzad /
NG0859:19123: dgung lo bcu gcig pa la dpal ldan 'bras spungs
NG0859:19124: su khams gsum pa'i gtsug gi nor bu kun gzigs
NG0859:19125: rgyal ba lnga pa'i drung du gtsug phud phul te
NG0859:19126: / mtshan ngag dbang pad+ma bstan 'dzin du bstsal /
NG0859:19127: skyi grong gi rang byung 'phags pa thog mar phebs
NG0859:19128: pa dang dus 'grigs pas gong nas rten 'brel bzang
NG0859:19129: zhes dgyes pas dbugs dbyung zhing */
NG0859:19130: de dus 'phags pa'i zhal zhi 'dzum chags pa'i nyams
NG0859:19131: gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od zer nyid kyi sku
NG0859:19133: bcu bdun pa la bsam yas su rje rgyal ba'i
NG0859:19134: dbang po mjal ba'i tshe spyan ras gzigs kyi rnam
NG0859:19135: par gzigs / rim par kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i dbang po lnga pa chen po dang */
NG0859:19136: yab rje gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub gnyis ni /
NG0859:19137: sku dngos kyis rjes su bzung ba'i bka' drin phul du byung bar ma zad /
NG0859:19138: phyis ye shes kyi skus kyang byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NG0859:19139: gnad kyis bka' drin mtshungs pa med pa'i rtsa ba'i
NG0859:19140: bla ma rnam pa gnyis dang */
NG0859:19141: gzhan yang smin grol zab lam gsan pa'i bstan 'dzin chen po bcu drug / zab chos sna @#//
NG0859:19142: tshogs gsan pa'i yongs 'dzin sum cu rtsa lnga rnams bsten te /
NG0859:19143: yul dus ci rigs par yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen /
NG0859:19145: sngar smos pa ltar bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs kyi dbang
NG0859:19146: brda don 'phrod pa thog ma'i smin byed du gsan
NG0859:19147: pas sdom pa gsum gyi gzhi bzung ste /
NG0859:19153: gshed skor sogs sngags 'gyur bka' ma deng sang rgyun yod do cog dang */
NG0859:19154: gter ma bla rdzogs thugs gsum sgrub sde spyi dang
NG0859:19155: bye brag gi bka' rigs mi 'dra ba du mas
NG0859:19156: mtshon yongs grags phal mo che /
NG0859:19158: sgrub thabs brgya rgyam sogs spyi bka' dang */
NG0859:19162: gshed skor kr-i yog sogs kyi zur bka' /
NG0859:19163: mdo phyogs mang po dang bcas pa'i dbang khrid bshad lung */
NG0859:19164: de thams cad kyi rtsa bar gyur pa bka' 'gyur

NG0859:19166: mtha' yas te ming tsam 'dzin pa'ang dka' ba'i gnas
NG0859:19167: so // dgung lo bcu gsum pa tsam nas bzung */
NG0859:19168: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po /
NG0859:19171: yid bzhin mdzod rtsa 'grel rnams thugs la bzung nas yab rje las gsung bshad rim par gsan cing */
NG0859:19172: phyis gnubs zur rong zom rnams kyi gsung rab dang */
NG0859:19173: sa skya pan+di ta'i rab dbye /
NG0859:19174: bcom ldan ral gri'i spyi rnams /
NG0859:19175: rang byung zhabs kyi nang don rnams kyang thugs la btsud cing */
NG0859:19176: khyad par kun mkhyen chen po'i gsung rab rnams la
NG0859:19177: gzigs rtogs nan tan mdzad pas blo gros kyis rnam
NG0859:19178: par dpyod pa'i mthu thogs pa med pa brnyes te
NG0859:19179: / ji snyed pa'i chos thams cad la sgro 'dogs chod /
NG0859:19180: dwags ston chos rgyal bstan 'dzin la 'dus pa mdo'i
NG0859:19181: dbang chog rin chen phreng ba'i steng nas dkyil 'khor
NG0859:19182: bzhi bcu rtsa lngar phye ba las chu+u bo bzhi
NG0859:19183: yongs rdzogs gtad rgya mtha' brten tshe dbang dang bcas
NG0859:19184: pa'i dbang gdams ngag bshad lung dang bcas pa dang
NG0859:19185: */ dbang chog sbrang rtsi'i chu rgyun gyi steng nas
NG0859:19186: dkyil 'khor nyi shu rtsa gcig ras bris la brten
NG0859:19187: par dbang lung gdams ngag dang bcas pa rnams gsan
NG0859:19188: */ / yang rdo rje drag rig 'dzin mchog gi
NG0859:19189: sprul pa'i skur dkyil 'khor nyi shu rtsa bdun du
NG0859:19190: bsdus pa'i rtsa dkyil ras bris dang de phyin tshom
NG0859:19191: bu la brten te dbang mchog rin chen phreng ba'i
NG0859:19192: thog nas dbang gdams ngag bshad lung dang bcas pa
NG0859:19194: gsang mtshan gnyis kas 'gyur med rdo rje rtsal du gsol /
NG0859:19195: smon lam gyi 'brel pa sad pas zab gter gyi bka' bab tshul kyang */
NG0859:19196: dgung lo bco brgyad pa chu yos zla ba lnga
NG0859:19197: pa'i tshe bcu la g.ya' ma lung nas rig 'dzin
NG0859:19198: thugs thig / nyer gnyis pa me lugs khrums zla'i
NG0859:19200: 'phrul gyi bkod pas shel brag nas gshin rje gshed dregs 'joms /
NG0859:19201: so gcig pa me 'brug stag zla'i nya la o
NG0859:19202: dkar brag nas gur drag dang rdor sems a ti'i
NG0859:19203: skor / so lnga pa lcags sprel chu stod zla
NG0859:19204: ba'i nyer dgu la sha 'ug ltag sgo nas thugs
NG0859:19205: rje chen po bde gshegs kun 'dus kyi chos skor
NG0859:19206: khrom gter du spyan 'dren par mdzad cing */
NG0859:19207: de dag gi snga phyi ci rigs par brag dmar mchims phu /
NG0859:19208: g.ya' ma lung sogs grub pa'i gnas chen ngo mtshar can rnams dang */
NG0859:19209: gdan sa gsar rnying gi gzim chung */
NG0859:19210: gzim spyil 'od gsal rtse dang bsam gtan rtse sogs
NG0859:19211: dben pa rnams su sku mtshams lo sbrel ma dang
NG0859:19214: zla gcig gis mtha' brten pa yan gyis /
NG0859:19215: bla ma zhi drag / rdor sems /
NG0859:19221: mkha' spyod ma sogs yi dam gyi lha sum cu rtsa lnga tsam gyi bsnyen sgrub dang */
NG0859:19222: rdzogs pa chen po khregs chod kyi nyams bzhes la snying por dril nas /
NG0859:19223: thod rgal dang rlung sbyor sogs kyang dus gnad dang bstun te thugs nyams su bzhes pas /
NG0859:19224: ma dag pa'i snang ba 'gog pa'i bskyed rim la brtan pa thob ste /
NG0859:19225: las bzhi gang yang thogs med du grub /
NG0859:19226: rdzogs rim rtsa rlung thig le'i 'gros d+hu tir dag pas zhu bde'i ye shes phyogs brgyar 'bar /
NG0859:19227: rdzogs pa chen po rang snang ris med kyi dgongs

NG0859:23297: de tsam du ma zad sangs rgyas rnams kyis 'jig

NG0859:23300: rer zhen cing */ mtha' gzhan la rmongs pa'i gtam
NG0859:23301: gzhung ba med par rang nyid kyis shugs 'byung du

NG0859:23306: bas mtha' gcig tu nges pa mi 'dug na'ang sngon
NG0859:23307: rjes kyi 'jug pa dag dgos pa gang gi ched
NG0859:23310: dus gsum gyi sgrub pa dang */
NG0859:23311: de la'ang spyir btang dmigs bsal /
NG0859:23312: snga phyi'i tshig sbrel ba'i mtshams sbyor /

NG0859:23315: kyis brda legs par sbyor ba'i legs bshad rnams dang

NG0859:23317: bcos chen po rtsa 'grel rnams kyi go ba dang
NG0859:23319: brda rnying pa yin nges kyi ming rnams sor bzhag dang yul phran so sor bsgyur stabs kyis sam /
NG0859:23320: rgyud tshan pa re la chos skad dang rang gi
NG0859:23321: thun mong min pa'i brda re yod pa lta bur
NG0859:23322: snang bas de rnams sor bzhag byas shing yul skad
NG0859:23323: shan shor ba lta bu'i ma dag nges pa rnams
NG0859:23324: dor / dpyad mi bzod pa'i rigs ni don gang
NG0859:23325: yin ma nges bzhin du 'ol tshod kyi bzo bcos
NG0859:23326: bgyis na rgyal ba'i bka' yang dag pa'i gnas la
NG0859:23328: don ji bzhin ma yin par gyur na bdud kyi
NG0859:23329: las su 'gyur pa'i phyir dpe mthun shas che ba
NG0859:23330: gtso bor byas pa nyid nyes chung bar rtogs nas
NG0859:23332: phal cher la phyis su rgyud sde gzigs pa'i mkhyen
NG0859:23333: pa can 'byung du re ba'i dpyad gzhir rtags kyis
NG0859:23334: gsal bar byas pa sogs snga phyi kun tu brda
NG0859:23335: sbyor la blta ba'i mig grung por gyur pa sngags
NG0859:23337: a srung sogs blo gsal gzhan gyis kyang lan mang
NG0859:23338: du bsgrags nas nan lcags thar gsum gyis zhu dag
NG0859:23339: bgyis shing rang nyid kyis kyang lan grangs du mar
NG0859:23340: nan tan gyis dpyad zhus kyis gtan la phab pa'i
NG0859:23342: grangs mang bas rdo rje tshig brling zhing rtogs dka' ba dang */
NG0859:23343: gsar ma'i rgyud rnams dang mi dra bar sngon nas
NG0859:23344: bzung da lta'i bar dag ther gyis ma phog pas
NG0859:23345: zhus dag tu btab kyang don la gzhi bsgrigs lta
NG0859:23346: bur dgos pas ma mo'i rgyud srid pa'i rdzong lung
NG0859:23347: dang e ka dza ti'i rgyud sogs la lan grangs
NG0859:23348: bco lnga nyi shu re bskyar zhus byed dgos byung
NG0859:23349: ba lta bus mtshon shin tu dka' ba'i gnas su
NG0859:23350: gyur kyang mdor na gsung rab kyi don ni tshig
NG0859:23351: la mi rton don la rton /
NG0859:23352: drang don la mi rton nges don la rton /
NG0859:23353: gang zag la mi rton chos la rton /
NG0859:23354: rnam shes la mi rton ye shes la rton pa
NG0859:23355: lhongs su ma gyur na sgra dang rtog ge'i rig
NG0859:23356: pa ni chos nyid dang 'gal ba'i chos can te
NG0859:23357: / gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de ni gang gi blo zhib pa /
NG0859:23359: shin tu zab pas blta bar bya'o //
NG0859:23360: gang la la dag chos thams cad la mu dang gting dang */
NG0859:23361: mtha' dang dbus 'tshol ba yod na de dag ni

NG0859:23363: / thug pa nyid du thug pa zhes bya'o //
NG0859:23364: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir thog mar sgra tshad la sogs
NG0859:23365: pa'i rig pas bsregs bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin du
NG0859:23366: zhib pa dang ches zhib par brtags nas //
NG0859:23367: mthar gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa ni don
NG0859:23368: gyi chos nyid dang mi 'gal bar chos su bzung
NG0859:23369: bar rjes su 'doms pa yin pas ji ltar dpyad
NG0859:23370: kyang mi 'gal ba'i shin tu zab pa'i phyogs kyang
NG0859:23371: cung zad mthong mod kyi skye bo drang don tsam
NG0859:23372: dang tshig la rtog dpyod 'jug pa gtso bor byed
NG0859:23373: pa dag gi dbang shes la'ang rgyud kyi tshig don
NG0859:23374: brling ba dang dpyad zhus mkhas po'i blo gros kyi
NG0859:23376: log par rtogs pa dang hor shor sogs gtan med
NG0859:23377: do zhes smra bar mi nus kyang sngon chad gangs
NG0859:23378: can 'dir dper rgyun yod pa rnams las khyad par
NG0859:23379: du 'phags shing yang dag par bgyis pas rnam par
NG0859:23380: dag pa'i bstan pa la mos pa rnams kyis yid
NG0859:23381: rton pa'i gnas su rung bar yod dam snyam mo
NG0859:23382: // bzhi pa bzhengs tshul dngos ni /
NG0859:23383: de'ang yi ge 'dus pa la ming */
NG0859:23384: ming 'dus pa tshig / tshig 'dus pa la tshigs
NG0859:23385: su bcad pa dang lhug pa sogs gzhung tshigs yi
NG0859:23386: ge'i rgyud du grub pa ste /
NG0859:23387: de la yi ge ni ming dang tshig gang yang
NG0859:23388: rung ba gsal bar byed pa'i phyir rjod byed thams
NG0859:23389: cad kyi rtsa bar gyur pa yin la /
NG0859:23390: gangs can gyi ljongs su 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa
NG0859:23391: thon mi sam b+ho ta'i mkhyen dpyod kyi 'phrul las
NG0859:23392: legs par thon pas bod yul gyi yi ge gsar
NG0859:23393: du 'khrungs pa nas bzung khyung po g.yu khris thig
NG0859:23394: gi lam du gcur zhing mkhas pa gzhan gyis lhan
NG0859:23395: thabs kyang mdzad pa'i rgyud las gdon pa bcu dang
NG0859:23397: chos nyi shu'i mtshan nyid rnam par bshad pa'i lag
NG0859:23398: khrid kyi rgyun ji lta bar sbyang bdar gyis khong
NG0859:23400: chen po'i gsung rab rin po che 'ba' zhig las
NG0859:23401: bzhengs pa mang po dag sngar phan bzhugs pa rnams

NG0859:23407: 'bu srin gyi rjes lta bur gyur pa sogs skyon
NG0859:23408: gyi rnam pa lan brgyar dpyad kyang dmigs par dka'
NG0859:23409: ba'i yig mkhan mkhas pa dag gi rgyun las byung
NG0859:23410: ba'i dpon yig pa sum cu skor gyi lhun grub
NG0859:23411: steng gi bla brang chen po'i bris khang du par
NG0859:23412: yig 'bri ba'i gra tshugs pa dang */
NG0859:23413: de bzhin du par brkos brgyad cu lhag dang */
NG0859:23414: zhus dag pa bcu skor dang */
NG0859:23417: snag las pa sogs las ka mkhan gyi rnam grangs
NG0859:23418: shin tu mang ba bar mtshams ma chad par bsags
NG0859:23419: shing */ de dag gis zhus dag bgyis zin pa dang par yig 'bri /

NG0859:23421: zhus dag byed mkhan rnams kyis lan gnyis re ste
NG0859:23422: bzhi bzhir zhus dag byas zin nas par brkos pa
NG0859:23423: rnams la so sor sprod pa sogs las spyi'i do
NG0859:23424: dam dang 'go lung ni mi'i dbang po'i zhabs rim
NG0859:23425: pa blo gzhung la tshugs thub pa /
NG0859:23426: khog yangs la dkyel che ba /
NG0859:23427: drang zhing g.yo sgyu dang bral bas chos sbyin mi
NG0859:23428: zad pa'i 'byung gnas par khang chen mo'i phyag mdzod
NG0859:23429: gu ru tshe brtan gyis bkod pas khyab pa bzhin
NG0859:23430: / gnyer byed pa ye shes dpal ldan dang */
NG0859:23432: par dngos gzhi phar sprod cing tshur len pa dang bskyar bzo dgos pa dang */
NG0859:23433: legs nyes blta rtogs sogs par dpon gyi bkod pa

NG0859:23443: bdud kyi ris su gyur pa'i gnod sbyin dang */

NG0859:23460: sbyor ba drag shul gyi cho ga dang */

NG0859:23475: gdon thams cad kyang sngags bdag mo dang khyab 'jug
NG0859:23476: chen po sogs srung ma chen po rnams kyis bsrungs
NG0859:23478: rab tu sba bar byas pa legs byas rgya chen

NG0859:23485: snyigs ma'i dus kyi mtha'i 'byung po ma rung pa'i

NG0859:23505: gzhan dag kyang ni mchod par bya //
NG0859:23507: nar ma'i bza' btung gi phogs dang */
NG0859:23508: las tshan so so'i yon dang par shing gi rin

NG0859:23524: gang gnas par bya ba gsum ka rnam par mi rtog pa'i gnas @#//
NG0859:23525: lugs rjes su dran pa tsam gyis de kho na nyid kyi rab tu gnas par 'gyur la /

NG0859:23534: gsungs shing mkhas pa'i gzhung nas bshad pa ltar tshang

NG0859:23547: tshab thar rtse zhal snga nas kyis dpal dgyes mdzad
NG0859:23548: rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i spyan dbye ba'i
NG0859:23549: cho ga bzang po drug dang ldan pa legs pa

NG0859:23553: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che'i rtsa lag tu

NG0859:23563: 'dir ni sa yi thig ler gyur //
NG0859:23564: snyan pa'i me tog dog pa ni //
NG0859:23565: yon tan dri bzangs tshogs 'dzin pa //
NG0859:23566: phyogs bral rig dwags mig can gyi //
NG0859:23567: rna ba'i rgyan du ci yang dar //
NG0859:23568: bka' rtags gser gyi cod pan ni //
NG0859:23569: sa skyong rnams kyi spyi bo ru //
NG0859:23570: phreng ba ji bzhin 'dzin byed na //
NG0859:23571: de ni de yi dpal gyis mdzes //
NG0859:23572: zhum pa med pa'i snying stobs 'khor lo yis //
NG0859:23573: chos las byung ba'i rig pa'i dpung khyer bas //

NG0859:23575: rdzogs ldan dang po'i skal bzang drangs par gyur //
NG0859:23576: sems ni rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rangs pas //
NG0859:23577: srid pa'i phun tshogs g.yon ma'i 'jo sgeg gi / tshor ba bde ba'i @#//
NG0859:23579: bsil ba'i khams su te por spyod la zhugs //

NG0859:23593: slong la dpag bsam long ba rnams kyi dmig bu lam gzhan dag la lam gyi rgyags //

NG0859:23595: mya ngan thang la mi bslu'i skyel ma chos dang 'dra ba'i mdza' bshes gzhan yod min //
NG0859:23596: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa thams cad kyi snying
NG0859:23597: po rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod theg pa snga
NG0859:23598: 'gyur rgyud 'bum rin po che'i rtogs pa brjod pa

NG0859:23601: snyed pa glegs bam zad mi shes pa'i phyi mor

NG0859:23603: pa'o /// / pra yo bi di ta ba sto
